1. Pathi mudhalaam mavathil, pathi yenakku koodamal,
Yethisayum uzhandru odi ilaithu vizhum kakam pol,
Muthi tharum nagar ezhil mukkiyamaam kachi thannil,
Athigiri arul aalarkku, adaikaalam naan pugundhene.
2. Chadai mudiyan, chathur mukanendru, ivar mudhalaam tharam yellam,
Adaya vinai payanagi, azhindu vidum padi kandu,
Idamudaya arulaalar, inay adikal adainthene.
3. Thanthirangal verindri thamathu vazhi azhiyaadhu,
Manthirangal thammalum, mathumulla urayalum,
Antharam kandu adi panivaar, anaivarkkum arul puriyum,
Sinthura ver piraiyavanaar, seelam allathu ariyene.
4. Kakam irakkadhan, mannar kadali kathira panthu,
Naga malai nayakanar nalladi podadainthene.
5. Ukakkum avai uhandhu, ukava anaithum ozhinthu, thuuravu guna,
Miga thunivu pera unarnthu, viyan kavalena varithu,
Jagathil oru pugal illa thavam ariyen mathi kachi,
Nagar karunai nathanai nalla adaikkalamy adainthene.
6. Alavudayar adaintharkkum, athan uraye kondavarkkum,
Valavurai thandhavan arule, manniya mathavathorkkum,
Kalavozhivaar amar yena, isainthavarkkum kavalaraam,
Thulava mudi arul varadar, thuvakkil yenai vaithene.
7. Umadhu adikal adaikendren yendru oru naal uraithavarai.
Amayum ini yenbavar pol, anjal yena karam vaithu,
Thamadhu anaithum avar thamakku vazhangiyum thaam miga vilangum,
8. Thinamai kuryamaikkum, niraikaikkum thee vinayaal,
Unmai maravamaikkum, ula mathiyil ugakkaikkum,
Thaami kazhiyamaikkum tharikkaikkukm, thanikkaikkum,
9. Surithi ninivu ivai ariyum, thunivudayor thoo mozhigal,
10. Thirumagalum, thiruvadivum, thiruvarulum, thellarivum,
Marumai ilamayum uravum, alappariya vadivarasum,
Karumam azhippu alippu amaippum, kalakkam ilaa vagai nindra,
Arul varadar nilai ilakkil, ambena naan amizhndene.
11. Aaru payan verilla adiyavar kal anaivarukkum,
Ma ru m athan payanum ivai oru kaalum pala kaalum,
Aaru payan yenave kandu, arul aalar adiyinai mel,
Kooriya narkunai uraigal, ivai pathum kothilave.

‘palaathkaarathukku ethiraaka sattam iyarrivittom, ini makankal poruppaaka irukka vendum’: pirathamar modi arivurai
pirathamar modi: koppuppadam
palaathkaarathai thadukka naankal sattam iyarrivittom, ini naattil ulla makankal(aankal)thaan poruppudan nadakka vendum enru pirathamar modi arivurai kurinaar.
pirathamar modiyaiyum kolai seyvom’ : vairalaana aadiyo: kaithaana kovai kunduvedippu kurravaali
ippadiyum thirudukiraarkal ushaar; payanpaattaalarkalukku theriyaamale ediem kaardu mulam panam suruttal: arasu maruthuvar udpada 4 per kaithu
paaliyal sampavankalukku naadaalumanram vithivilakkalla; ithuvoru kasappaana unmai: kaankiras munnaal em.pi. renukaa sauthri petti
smith, vaarnar illaathathaal aasi.yai inthiya ani veelthum enru ninaippathai verukkiren: maikkel kilaark

appothu Avalukku Unarchi Athikamaaka Aarampam Aakum. Pinpu Kaikalaal Mulaiyai Nanraaka Methuvaaka Thadavi Pinpu Veekamaaka Alutthi Piseya Veendum Pinpu Avalin Pavadai Naadaavai Aviltthu Athai Kaladda Veendum. Pinpu Avalin Mukatthil Irunthu Muttham Athaavathu Uchanthalai Muthal Konjam Konjamaaka Mulaikalil Muttham Kodutthu Appadiyee Vayiru, Thoppul Aakiya Idatthila Muttham Kodutthu Thadavi Appadiyee Naakkaal Nakki Nakki Kondee Pundai In Mudiyai Kaikalaal Thadava Veendum. Appothu Pundai Pilavin Meel Ulla Paruppu Ay Viralkalaal Meelum Kilum Saidu Pakkamum Methuvaaka Thadavinaal Avalukku Innum Soodu Athikamaaka Irukkum. Appothu Viralkalai Paruppu In Kil Ulla Pilavin Ulla Oddai Ila Nadu Viralin Munaiyai Vaitthu Ullum Veliyum Pala Murai Seythu, Pinpu Antha Pundai Meedin Pakuthi Il Oru Muttham Kodutthu Pinpu Pundai Meedin Mudi Ulla Idatthila Thavangoddai Vaitthu Konjamaaka Thaadi Vaitthu Irunthu Thadavinaal Rompa Sukamaaka Irukkum. Pinpu Avalin Pundai In Paruppai Naakkaal Valathum, Idathum, Meelum, Kilum Vaitthu Naakkin Munpuram Vaitthu Thadavinaal Rompa Arputhamaa Irukkum.
(Pundaiyai Nakkuvathu Eppadi? Enra Kadduraiyaip Paarkka Sellavum.)
appothu Paruppu Jiv Jiv Enru Unarchi Udan Irukkum. Appothu Aval Unnudaiya Thalaiyai Piditthu Innum Nanraaka Soopparaa Nakkudaa ..soopparaa Nakkudaa ….. Enru Unarchi Thathumpa Solluvaal. Pinpu Pundai In Kil Ulla Pilavu Ulla Idatthila Irandu Kaalaiyum Viritthu Vaitthu Pundai Il Unnudaiya Mukam Vaitthu Alutthi Athil Ulla Oddaiil Naakku Munai Vaitthu Nanraaka Nakka Veendum Appothu Aval Unarchi Innum Athikamaaka Irukkum Appothu Pundai Il Irunthu Oru Thiravam Varum Athai Appadiyee Athai Suvaitthaal Rompa Soopparaa Irukkum. Ithu Maathiri Seyyum Pothu Mulaikalai Irandu Kaikalaal Appadiyee Thadavi Kodukka Veendum Rompa Nallaa Irukkum.
athan Pinpu Avalai Unnudaiya Sunni Yai Kaikalaal Thadavi Athai Thaddi Kodutthu Eluppa‌ Veendum. Avalin Kaikalai Sunni In Meel Vaitthu Munnum Pinnum Tholai Thalla Solla Veendum Appothu Sunni Nanraaka Deempeer Aka Aarampam Aakum Appothu Avalai Vaay Vaitthu Sunni In Mun Puram Ulla Pilavu Ulla Idatthila Avalin Naakku Nuni Vaitthu Meelum Kilum Valathu Idathu Enru Ellaa Pakkamum Naakkai Vaitthu Methuvaaka Sularra Sollavum. Appothu Sunni Sooppar Aka Jiv Jiv Jiv Enru Thudikkum. Appothu Uchanthallai Muthal Paatham Varai Unarchi Pongi Valiyum. Antha Nilai Rompa Nallaa Irukkum.
appothu Ivarukkum Nallaa Mood Vanthavudan Avalin Pundai Paruppin Meel Sunni Yai Vaitthu Thadava Veendum Appothu Sunni Innum Athikamaaka Deempeer Aakum Pinpu Avalin Irandu Kaalkal Meelee Thookki Unnudaiya Sunniya Pundai Pilavu Oddai Il Vaitthu Alutthinaal Athu Ullee Pokum Appothu Vali Konjam Irukkum Atharku Konjam Theengaay Ennai Vaitthal Sulapamaaka Ullee Pokum Appothu Munnum Pinnum Unnudaiya Udampai Asaitthu Asaitthu Seythaal Rompa Rompa Rompa Rompa Sukamaaka Irukkum Appothu Avalin Savund Rompa Nallaa Irukkum Athaavathu Hamming Savund Varum Ithu Maatri Seythaal Sirithu Neeratthil Uchakaddam Adainthu Pinpu Unnudaiya Sunni Il Irunthu Kanji Vellai Niratthil Avalin Pundaikkul Senru Vidum Ithu Thaan Udal Uravu Seyum Murai.

enna 12 Moodanampikkaikalaip Parriyum Paditthuviddeerkalaa. Sari Intha 12 M Thavarenraal Ethu Unmai Ena Ariyum Aaval Eerpaddaal Kilee Sellungal.
1. Aanuruppin Alavirkum Kalavikkum Sammanthamillai. Irandu Ins Alavu Pennuruppirkul Athu Senruviddaalee Vinthanu Neenthis Senru Andatthinai Adainthuvidum.
2. Viraippu Enpathu Ratthanaalangalin Moolamaaka Aanuruppinaal Eerpadukinrathu. Pothumaana Ichaikku Aan Aadpadum Pothu Thaan Ithu Nikalum.
3. Aanuruppu Elumpinaal Aanaathu Alla. Melliya Thasaikalaal Aanaathu , Appadiyirukka Eppadi Irumpaaka Maarum.
4. Viraikal Samamaaka Irunthaalthaan Piradsanai. Perumpaalum Idathu Viraiyaanathu Sarru Kilee Kaanappadum. Ithan Ariviyal Kaaranam Irandu Viraikalum Onrodu Onru Urasikkollaamal Vipatthil Maaddikkollaamal Irukka Veendum Enpathee.

7. Suyainpam Seythu Veliyeerraaviddaal Nadakkum Iyarkai Nikalvu Ithu. Ungal Veeddil Moddaar Poddu Thannirai Thoddikku Anuppukireerkal. Thannir Thoddi Nirampiyapin Valinthaal, Athai Thavaru Enpeerkalaa. Ungalukku Pathil Vinthai Iyarkaiyee Veliyeerri Vidukirathu. Avvalavuthaan.
8. Unarchikal Ullavan Thaanee Manithan. Avanukku Ellaa Vakaiyaana Unarvukalum Thonrum. Kaamamum Iyalpaana Unarchi. Ellaa Neerangalilum Kopam Varumaa. Varaathu Athu Pola Thaan Kaamamum.
9. Ippadiyellaam Kadhaikal Thaan Solla Mudiyum.unmaiyil Nadakkaatha Kaariyam Ithu.
10. X Aan,pen Iruvarum Seernthu Seykinra Seyal. Oruvarudaiya Pangillaamal Marravarkalaal Thirupthi Adaiya Iyalaathu.
11. Chitthiramum Kaippalakkam Enru Solvaarkal. Palaka Palaka Ellaam Sariyaakum. Muthal Muraiyil Mokam Veendumaanaal Thaniyalaam Enkiraar Maatroo.

Aktopar 2011 l, rasya 16 mutal 14 varai stetiyankalai ennikkai kuraittatu. Masko pakutiyil munmoliyappatta Podolsk stetiyam kattumana pirantiya aracankattal rattu ceyyappattatu, melum talainakaril, Otkrytiye Arena tinamo stetiyam pottiyitum itu mitu kattappattatu mutal. 2012 Ceptempar 29 am tikati host nakarankalin irutit tervu arivikkappattatu. Nakarankalin ennikkai 11 akavum, stetiyam ennikkai 12 akavum, krasnotar marrum yaroslavl akiyavarrin iruti pattiyalil iruntu nikkappattana. Oru Spekulatthai En Saamaanukkul Nulaitthu Edutthu Etho Parisothitthaal. Pin Ennidam “maathavi Ellaam Naarmalaatthaan Irukku. Onnum Payappada Veenaam. Aanaal Ennadi Un Vejinaa Oddai Rompa Daiddaa Irukku. Aaru Maatham Purusan Koodap Padukkaamal Irunthaa Ippditthaan Irukkum” Enraal. Naan “enna Solree Jos” Enratharku Aval “aamaadi.. Ippadi Nirai Maasamaa Irukkum Pothu Deyli Seyyanumdi. Appatthaan Delivari Isiyaa Irukkum” Enraal. Naan Eerkanavee Itthanai Naal Joli Paarkkaamal Ulloora Eengip Poy Iruntheen. Ippothu Ival Veeru Ippadi Solkiraalee Enru Ninaitthapadi “aamaa.. Athukkenna Panrathu. En Purusan Vayitthula Eetthiddu ஃpaarin Poyiddaaru.. Naan Enna Panrathu-” Enreen. Josaஃpin Oru Maathiri Siritthapadi “m.. Nee Sarinnaa Sollu 8230 Un Saamaan Oddaiyaip Perisaakka Naan Aalu Eerpaadu Seyyareen” Enravudan Enakku Athirchiyaaka Irunthathu. Ival Purushanum Daakdarthaan. Naan Paartthirukkeen. Aal Rompa Sdailaaka Iruppaar. Avar Enakku Purushanaaka Amaiyavillaiyee Enru Sila Samayam Ninaippathu Undu. Athanaal Naan Manasukkul Oruveelai Aval Purushanai Viddu Ennai Seyyas Solvaalo Enru Ninaippu Vanthathu. Naan Thayakkatthudan “enna Solree Jos.. Un Haspandu Koodap Padukkas Solriyaa-” Enreen. Aval Siritthapadi “m..mhoom En Haspandai Unakku Sheer Pannikka Vida Maaddeen. Athukku Veera Aal Irukku. En Lavvar Orutthan Mukeeshnu Irukkaan. Avanukku Thadi Irumpu Ulakkaiyaa Irukkum. Avan Deyli Unnaip Poddaannaa Un Oddai Nallaa Virinju Kodutthirum. Ennadi Avanai Varas Sollavaa-” Enraal. Unakkuk Kurumputhaan” 8230 .. “sarivaa Kilinikku Vaa.. Unakku Puthusaa Oru Prasand Tharapporeen” 8230 “m.. Ennavaa.. Ellaam Unakkup Pidichathuthaan Vaa” Enraal. Pin Aval Kansalding Roomin Pinpuram Iruntha Resd Roomil Ennai Irukkas Solli Viddu Mithi Ulla Peeshandukalai Paartthu Anuppividuvathaakas Sonnaal. Thappu Seyvathaa Enru Oru Kurra Unarchi Irunthaalum Itthanai Naal Okkaatha Pundai En Manasaadsiyai Miri Arikkat Thodangiyathu. Oru Mani Neeram Kalitthu Josaஃpin Antha Mukeeshudan Ullee Vanthaal. Nallaa Avalai Enjaay Pannu” Enrapadi Avan Aadaikalai Avilkka Ithuvarai En Purusan Saamaanai Maddumee Paartthiruntha Enakku Avan Thandu Kodimaramaaka Neelamaaka Needdik Kondiruppathaik Kandathum En Thodaiyidukku Kasiya Aarampittthu. Ennaiyum Aval Ammanamaakka Naan Periya Paanai Vayirraik Kaaddiyapadi Sopaavil Kidakka Josaஃpin Ammanamaaka Aanaal. Pin En Pundaiyil Spekulatthai Soruki Irandu Moonru Murai Kutthi Edutthaal. Pin Mukeesh En Pundaikkul Methuvaaka Avan Sunniyai Nulaikka Padu Irukkamaaka Irukka Naan Thodaiyaip Polanthu Kondu Kidantheen. En Pundaikkul Daiddaaka Nulaintha Avan Sunniyai Varudiyapadi Josaஃpin Rasitthuk Kondirunthaal. Pin Moonru Peerum Appadiyee Ammanamaakk Kidanthom. Josaஃpin “maathavi.. Nee Otthathaip Paattthum Enakkum Aasaiyaayirukkudi. Naan Okkavaa-” Enraal. Naan Kalakalaven Siritthu “eey.. Avaru Un Lavvar. Periyasamy Sivagnanam:-

Tamil dialect la, English script la oru post pottu romba naal aachu... "Idhu pudikkala", "Idhu tamila damage pannudhu" nu sila tamil aarva iyakkangal poarkodi uyarthirukkanga. Paravalla. Tamil la sariyana ல ள verupaadu kandupudichu dabba dabbava kaattadha internet ennikku varudho, anniku naan tholkaappiya tamil la ezhudharen.
Vaazhkaila saagaradhukkulla ellarum sila kaaryangal pannanum. Maram nadanum, oru aezhaikku soru podanum, Kovil/Ulaga sutrupayanam poganum... Adhukkellam munnadi irukku oru Chennaivaasiyoda sila adhyavasya thevaigal. Idhellam seiyyala na avan aathma shanthi adaiyadhu. For example
At least oru padathoda preview show aiyavadhu paathudanum [apdiye anga actors lam vandhiruppanga. Avangakitta autograph, photograph vanganum]
Oru match avadhu Chepauk la poi pakkanum. Anga match oda categorya poruthu CSK vukko, Indian teamukko support panra madhiri oru 10 rooba thoppiya 100 rooba kuduthu vaanganum. Kannathula colour adichukkanum. Anga irukkara periya TV la namma moonji theriyanum [Adhukkaga oru azhagana ponnu pakkathula seat pudikkanum]
Suburban train tracka foot overbridge la cross pannama unauthoriseda level cross pannanum. Anga namakkagave arasanga sottha paazh paduthi oruthan sevuttha odaichu vechiruppan. Adhu vazhiya naama poi sariya 50 seconds michappaduthanum [MRTS/CMRL la apdi panna mudiyadhu]

Indha varisai la ippo recenta join aayirukku MALLS. Nammoorula Oru 100 varusham munnadi Spencer Plaza nu onnu kattinanga. Adhukkum adhukku adutha mall kum idaila podhiya idaiveli [several decades] vittu dhan kattirukkanga. Bangalorela irukkara madhiri ovvoru muttusandhu pillayar kovil pakkathuliyum oru mall kattala. Idhunaliye Mallgalaala chennai makkal [unnmaiyana Chennai kudimagangal] romba perisa baadhippadaiyala. Sila pala mistakes ku aprom EA, Ampa Skywalk [ippo Phoenix] ellam vandhudhu.

EA ku idhu enakku 3rd time. Spencer Plaza ku oru vaatti poyirukken [chinna vayasula, appa kooda]. Avlo dhan. 'Mall' vaasam padama potthi potthi valarkkappattavan. EA ku varradhukku best vazhi personal transport dhan. Bike la kaiya oru thiruppu thiruppinom na konjam petrol kudichuttu vandi nammala 20 minutes la kondu vandhu sethudum. Enakkum andha 20 minutes kum irukkara dhooram andha bike dhan [Evernote la 'Bike vaanganum' nu oru checklist la pottu 1 varusham aachu]. "Varum... Aana varadhu" style la iyangara MTC bus pudichu Guindy, angirundhu TVS estate la iranganum. High court bus vandha nama senja punnyam. Adhuvum nama stop ku vandha udane vandhaa namma appa amma senja punnyam. So, 1 mani neram munnadiye kelambinen. Bus vandha time vecchu paatha naanum punyam pannala, enga appa ammavum punnyam pannala.
10 nimisham munnadi dhan yebhi.com la order panna shoe delivery pannanga. En mudhal sports shoe [well, branded one] voda mudhal boni idhu dhan. EA la naan romba edhirpakkaradhu azhagana ponnunga, oralavu decenta dress pannitu varuvanga. Adha vida romba edhirpakkaradhu breakups. First time vandhapodhu oru breakup- ponnu sogama poitta. Inniku EA vandha podhu suda suda oru breakup. Ponnu gettha sevuthula saanjuttirukka. Paiyyan O nu azhudhutte nadandhu veliya poraan. Bhaarathiyaar paatha peruma paduvar.

"Sir, Inga oru book launch ceremony nadakkudhe, adhu endha floor la?" nu oru security officera ketten. Avan "what?" apdeennaan. Adhu seri. Inneram maedaila aeri pesittiruppanga. Cha! Innum evlo per varuvanga?" nu angirundha en classmate Raghu kitta ketten. "Therla da. Oru 10 per varuvanga" nu sonnan. Aana innum konjam kooda santhoshappatrukkalam. Adhukkum kaaranam irukku. Mudhal kuzhandha porandha kooda GS tension aagiruppar, tired aagirukka maattaar. Kitta thatta idhu avarukke prasavam madhiri. Vanakkam Iyya,
Thozhil/vyabaram seivatharku - lagnathipathi + 10aam athipathi + 11 aam athipathi valuvaaga iruka vendum
Lagnathipathi - sukkran 8il , navasamathil aatchi balam petraalum + sevvai + neecha kethu kootu
10aam athipathi - Intha lagnathirku yoga kaaragana aana saniswaran - Lagnathil + sevvai(7&12 athipathi udan) kootu - navamsathil - Uchha budhan + saniswaran, Sevvai vargothamamam
11aam athipathi - Guru bhagavan ( Lagnathirku 4 il - 11 am veetirku 6 il ullar)
2 aam veetirku athipathi budhan 8il amarnthalum avanin neradi paarvai 2aam veetiruku ullathu + navamsamthil ucham + yoga kaaraganudan kootu
Budhan nandraga irunthaal thaan vyabaram seiya mudiyum + dasa buthiyum atharku etra vaaru iruka vendum
Jaathagarku aarambam ragu dasa (Sadayam 1 aam paatham) - aduthathu guru dasa - guru 8aam athipathiya irunthalum endrum nallavare - 4 aam veetil amarnthu suga jeevanathirku vazhi seithu ullar, melum 10aam veetirku - saniswaran + guruvin paarvai ullathu
Jaathagar vyabaram seiahlaam velaiku sella avasiyam illai.
guru dasa, yoga kaargan dasa budha dasa endru - varisayaga nalla dasaigal nadai peruvaathal , melum jaathagaruku 2,5, guru + yogakaargan saniswaran paarvai balamaga ullathal vyabaram nandra nadai perum

marupatiyum konjam sakdhi koota kotuththu en poolai azhuththinen. ippodhu paadhi pool maami puntaikkul poi vittadhu. kaamesh paththiyaa paadhi sunni poivittadhu. innum oru murai kuththu muzhu sunni en puntaikkul poivitum appuram nee kuththalaam kutaiyalaam. maami sonnavutan innum konjam palam kontu en sunniyai aval puntaiyil irakkinen. okkare aachchariyam. en thati aval koodhikkul muzhuvadhum poi ataikkalam aaki vittadhu. en pool maami puntaiyil maraththil aappu atiththadhu pola rompavum taittaaka irundhadhu. kaamesh, medhuvaa konjam un poolai veliye izhuththu thirumpavum innum konjama pirashar kotuththu ulle thallu. naalu murai idhu pola panninaal en puntai akantu vitum. unakku okka siramam irukkaadhu. maami sonnadhu pola seydhen. konjam konjamaaka aval puntai akalamaachchu. Tamil Mulai Paal Kamakathaikal.
ippo en sunni aval kukaiyil sulapamaaka poi vandhadhu. avalin paasikalai pitiththukontu avalai ippo okka thotanginen. maami munpu polave medhuvaaka aanaal raakam pottu munakinaal. en kuththu jaasdhiyaa irukkumpodhu maami konjam savunt koottinaal. naan enjin pistan pola oththu kontu irundhen. podhuvaaka kai atikkum podhu ettu alladhu paththu murai poolai uruvittaale enakku kanji vandhu vitum. anaal ippo maami puntaiyil kuththiyum kanji varavillai. innum konjam palam kootti kuththinen. maamikku valichchadhu pola irundhadhu. aiyo kaamesh ennamaa okkarataa nee . enga aaththukaararum irukkarare. naalu kuththu kudhi thanni thelippaar. ennai maadhiri puntai veri pitidhavalukku irupadhu kuththu vaanginaalum poradhutaa. enakku innum puriyaadha pudhir. Tamil Aunty Mulai Kathai.
Tamil Mulai Paal Kamakathaikal
kalyaanam aaki maamaa appovum idhupola thaan naalu kuththu kuththu kanji vittaar. eppitidhaan ponnu pirandhaalo. naanum kalyaanam aanaa podhu elloraiyum pola thaan irundhen. konjam konjamaaka en puntai veri jaasdhiyaaka aarampiththu vittadhu. en pirent kamalaannu oruththi aval kanavan oppadhai patri rompa peedhi koluvaal. eppati ellaam avalai oththaar endru kadhai solluvaal. aval pechchai kettu kettu enakku andha maadhiri veri vandhu vittadhu. veri vandhu pirayojanam illai . indha maadhiri maamaa irundhaa onnum natakkaadhu. unakku onnu solren kettukko.
eppodhumpola maamaa oththu vittu thookivitumaamiyin indha veri pechchai kettu naan innum palam kontu kuththinen. maami idhukkul rentu murai uchcham ataindhu madhana neerai veliyetrinaa. aval kaama neeril en sunni nanaindhadhaal, ulle poi vara kashtame illaamal irundhadhu. innum naalu kuththu kudhi avalpuntaiyil en kanjiyai peechchi atichchen. idhu varai kai atiththapodhu varaadha alavukku ipppo kanji vandhadhu. maami rompa thirupdhi endraal. maami sonnaal. kaamesh poradhutaa. innum moonu naalu murai okkanum. konjam rest etuththukkontu okkalaam. kanji ulle pochchunnu nee kavalai pataadhe. Tamil Mulai Paal Kamakathaikal.
endha pompilaikku indha alavukku kaaji irukko avalukku evvalavu kanji puntaikkul ponaalum onnum aakaadhu. preknant aakave maattaal. adhanaal nee kavalai pataamal innum oththu en puntaiyil un kanjiyai kottu. andru iravu maamiyai meentum moonu murai oththen. maamaa ooril irundhu vandha pinnum thotarndhadhu. Tamil Aunty Mulai Kathai.
Tamil Kudumba Kamakathaikal (Amma Magan) பெரியம்மாவுடன்

Makkal Kural Daily News
Kadavul Mangala Vizha
60. SIVALOGA SUNDARA MAALAI 10
ith thiruppadhiham mudhal mandalaththaich saarndhadhaahum. idhil muppadhu paadalhal ullana. ovvoru paadalaiyum oru malaraahak kondu muppadhu malargalaal oru paamaalai thoduththu adhatrkuch sivaloaha sundharamaalai yenap peyar soottiyullaargal. sivaloaha sundharanae yenru ovvoru paadalin irudhiyilum viliththullaargal. sivaloahaththil mikka azahudaiyavan muruhanae! aadhalaal azahu yennum porultharum sollaana sundharam yenbadhaiyae muruhan peyaraaha vaiththuch sundharanae yenru azaikkiraargal. andhach sundharanukkuch soottappetrra paamaalai aadhalaal sivaloaha sundharamaalai yena iththirupthihaththitrku peyar soottiyullaargal.
innoolil siththaandha selvar, arunootrpulamai aanroar paeraasiriyar daakdar pa. iraaman, avargalin vazihaattudhal peyaril ip paadal yennaip poal yeliyavar padippadhatrku yeatrravaaru piriththum andha paadalhalukku vilakkangalum kodukkappattulladhu. ivvaaru piriththu koduppadhu yeliya muraiyil katrruk kolluvadhatrku mattum thaan payanbaduththappada vaendum.
sivaloaha sundharanae! nyaayiru, thingal, sevvaai, pudhan, viyaazan, velli, sani, iraahu, kaedhu yennum navahoalhalum oliyudaiya naalil ulla palavahaiyaana kaalangalum (iraahu, yemahandam, kulihai poanravai) piravi yennum periya thunbaththai ozikkum un adiyaargalakkuth thaevaiyaana nanmaihalaich seiyumanri oruboadhum thunbaththaich seiyamaattaa. arivilaardhaam koalhalinaalum naatkalil varum ketta kaalangalinaalum thamakkuth thunbam vaaraadhirukkap parihaaram seivaargal. naalum, koalum nallavargalai yen seyum?
siththa vilai vaikkavarum sivaloaha sundharanae. 2.
yen ullaththin seyalaikkavarum sivaloaha sundharanae! pakthargalukkum, yoahihalukkum maelaana sivanyaanihatkum poi illaadha mei arulaahiya selvaththai aliththu aatkollumiraivan nee. paiththiyamaana adiyaenai aatkollaamal sirumaiyil vaippaayoa?
siththiraththai naan maravaen sivaloaha sundharanae. 3.
sivaloaha sundharanae! yeththanaiyoa vahai theivangalum yeththanaiyoa vahaiyaana seiyappaduhinra vinaihalum yeththanaiyoa vahaiyaana samayangalum ivvulahil ullana. yennai aththanaiyilum viruppam kollach seiyaamal un arulaiyae naadum vaziyil sellumaaru seidhanai. andha azahiya karunaiyai naan yenrum marakkamaattaen.
sellum alavu unai maravaen sivaloaha sundharanae. 4.
sivaloaha sundharanae! kal, irumbu, aahiyavatrraik kaattilum valimaiyum kadinamumaana vairam aana yen manaththai nanmai tharum thiruvarulai virumbumbadi adakkivitta un karunaiyinaal pahalum iravum yen irandu kangalum neeraippoziya ulla, paei poanra izindhavanaahiya naan irakkum kaalam varai unnai marakkamaattaen.
theeya manam vaakku udambil seidha maraththaal malam un
theeya arulyeri moottum sivaloaha sundharanae. 5.
urudhiyaana paavanaasam yennum sangaara kiruththiyanae! sivaloaha sundharanae! manaivi, makkal, aasai yenkinra paeigal pidiththu ivvulahil aattivaikkaamal yennai ivvaasaihalil irundhu pirikka yen ahaththil yezundharulip pahal iravaahath thondargal puhazndhuraikkum un perumaiyaich solla vaiththa unnai naan marakkamaattaen.
then ilangu thaesuudaiyaai sivaloaha sundharanae. 7.
azahu vilangum oli udaiyavanae, sivaloaha sundharanae! minnalaip poanru thoanri maraiyum ivvulaha aasai yenappadum poiyaana vaazvai ninaiththu unnai ninaikkaamal ingu nalla vidhiyai izandha naan vaazum poruttuth thiruvulam kondu innaalil un pakkam yennai izuththatrkuk konda anbinai naan marakkamaattaen.
pakkam adhai naan vilahap paarppaenoa kanbaaraai
sikkam aru selvam mali sivaloaha sundharanae. 8.
uriyai arukkum arutchelvam mihundha sivaloaha sundharanae! mei, vaai, kan, mookku, sevi yennum aimborihal yennum paavi yekkaalaththum iruppadhatrku thookkaahap payanbatta yennai vidudhalai seidhu adimai konda anbinai naan vilahich sellap paarpabaenoa? thirukkannoakkam seidharulvaayaaha!.
thinniya kanangal thozum sivaloaha sundharanae. 9.
thinmaiyaana kanangal vanangum sivaloaha sundharanae! yennudhatrku ariya kutrramudaiya naaipoanra atrpanaahiya yennai onrum seiyamaattaa. yennai nerungi varum anbu uruvam yekkaalaththum nilaiyaaha ulla punniya moorththiyae! unnai marappadhatrku yen puththi ini oththuk kollumoa? kollaadhu.
thiru irundha yezilnilavum sivaloaha sundharanae 10.
theivaththanmai irundha azahu vilangum sivaloaha sundharanae! oppumaiyillaadha arinyar uraiyaana nyaanam yendha alavum illaamal ariyaamai irundha irudhayamae mihundhirukka irundha naan vaazum poruttup peruhum anbai unmeedhu peruhumbadi vaiththa iraivanaahiya unnai naan marakka maattaen.
thendan iduvaar paravum sivaloaha sundharanae. 11.
vananguvaar thudhikkum sivaloaha sundharanae! thirumaal, piraman, indhiran, vaanoar, perumthavaththoar kandu alavidatrku ariya perumai udaiya nee yeliyaenaahiya yennaiyum thondan aakkiyamaikku naan mutrpirappil yenna thavam seidhaenoa?
thael yenum un adimaravaen sivaloaha sundharanae. 12.
sivaloaha sundharanae! kaalamaaha iruppavan nee. naal anaiththum iyamanudaiya naal yenru periya manaththil ninaikkaamal than nilaihettu arivumayangi maranam adaiyum manamudaiya ariyaamaik kurudar vazikku yennai anniyamaaha vaiththuk kaaththaruliya kadavulaana un thiruvadiyai yenrum maravaen.
then avirum yemmaanae sivaloaha sundharanae. 13.
thirukkarunaikku yenmaaru sivaloaha sundharanae. 14.
sivaloaha sundharanae! amarndhirukkum nilaiyilum ninru kondirukkum nilaiyilum iruhangalai moodith thoongum nilaiyilum manmael nadakkum nilaiyilum, kan, kaadhu, vaai aahiyavai paarththal, kaettal, paesudhal alladhu unnudhal yennum seyalhalaich seiyum nilaiyilum, pasiyaal vaadi unavu unnum nilaiyilum unnai maravaadhu ninaikkach seidhulla un azahiya karunaikku naan yenna kaimmaaru seivaen?
theivam yelaam thani thudhikkum sivaloaha sundharanae. 15.
saetta arul urimaiyinaal sivaloaha sundharanae. 16.
unnudaiya maenmaiyaana arul urimaiyinaal sivaloaha sundharanae! yeattil ulla yezuththukkalaith thakkabadi onru saerththu iyatrchollaaha aakka ariyaadha arivillaadha atrpanaahiya naan paattukkalinaal unnaiththudhikka oppillaadha oru paakkiyaththaip petrraen. anriyum, veedubaetrrai ninaiththu nanku pizaikkavum periya nyaanaththaiyum petrraen.
sidhalai thavirththu yenai aalum sivaloaha sundharanae. 17.
siththiraththaik kaatti arul sivaloaha sundharanae. 18.
sivaloaha sundharanae! poiyum poraamaiyum koodum indhak kalihaalaththil paiththiyamaana yennai aatkolla vandha yem kadavulae! yem iraivanae! thinamum unnai naan marakka maattaen. nee vaeru naan vaeru alla yenra oru vadivaththai yenakkuk kaattiyarulvaayaaha.
setrram ilaach sivakkozundhae sivaloaha sundharanae. 19.
yenrum azivillaadha sivakkozundhae! sivaloaha sundharanae! katrradhanaal undaana arivaiyum kaettadhanaal undaana arivaiyum veenaahach suduhaattitrkuk kondu poahaamal kalvi kaelvihalaal arindhu konda iraivanukku anbu seiya vaendum yena unarndhu unakku anbu seidhu yeppoadhum unnai ninaiththatrkuriya nanmaiyai naan petrradhuboal un thiruvadiyitr kalandhu vaazum vaazvu perach siridhalavaenum kadaikkan paarththu arulvaayaaha.
siththamisai kudihonda sivaloaha sundharanae. 20.
yen manaththil yezundharuliyulla sivaloaha sundharanae! paththi maarkkaththai kadaippidiththu uyarnilai adaiyaadhaar maranam varappoahinradhae yenru payandhu payandhu saavaargal. pakthiyudan iraivanai manaththil thiyaaniboar nyaanam petrru uyarndhu vetrri vetrri yenru koori iraivan thiruvadiyaich saervaar. (iyaman ulahu sellamaattaar) anudhinam unnai ninaiththu innum adaiya mudiyavillaiyae yennum varuththam maelidak kaththiyum, manam uruhiyum vaadum yennaich satrru un kadaikkannaal paarththarulvaayaaha.
siriyaenaith thaedi vandha sivaloaha sundharanae. 21.
saeruyearu mana tharavaam sivaloaha sundharanae. 22.
then adiyaar thirumudhalae sivaloaha sundharanae. 23.
yeliyaenin aadharavaaha ullavanae! azahiya adiyaarudaiya theivamudhatrporulae! sivaloaha sundharanae! nanmai mihundha thiruppazani malaiyai virumbich senradaiya ninra yennaith thaduththu “unnai innanaalil varuha yenru azaippaen, appoadhu nee varalaam, adhuvarai nee varakkoodaadhu” yenru sonna vaakkinbadi nee azaikka unakku adimaiyaana naan unnaik kaanavarunaal innanaal yenru idhuvaraiyilum naan ariyaenae!
thaerunaraip parandhu arulum sivaloaha sundharanae. 24.
seenam ilaap perundhahaiyae sivaloaha sundharanae. 25.
kaanum perumai undaahumoa? yennaik kaaththarulum arulai yenakku aliththu unnaip piriyaadha nilaiyil vaiththarulvaayaaha.
seyir inri nilava arul sivaloaha sundharanae. 26.
thandhai sudhanae yenra tharunam avan yean yean yenru
sindhai mahizndhu arulvadhu yennaal sivaloaha sundharanae. 27.
sivaloaha sundharanae! thandhai aana viyaasamunivar mahanae! yenra poadhu angu “yean? yean? yenru aahaayaththoadu sedi marangal yedhiroliththana. amala muththi yenru koorappadum patrrillaap pooranaththai adaindhavarum yennillaadhavar aavar. adhuboal yenakkuth thiruvulam mahizndhu pooranaththuvaththai arulvadhu yennaal?
seer anaiththum ullavanae sivaloaha sundharanae. 28.
nalla sirappukkal anaiththum ullavanae! sivaloaha sundharanae! kaaranam aziyaamal irukka adhanaal undaahum kaariyam aana poiyai oziththu andhak kaaranaththai naan arindhuhondu yennuvadhatrku mudiyaadhach samburanaththai adaivadhatrku ini arulpurivadhu yekkaalamoa?
theiva mudhaal saivamsei sivaloaha sundharanae. 29.
yengalai adimaihonda theivamaana mudhatrporulae! saivaththaich seiyum sivaloaha sundharanae! saivam yennum sol sivaththodarpu yenap porul tharuvadhatrku oru siridhum aiyam illai. aadhalaal un adiyaenaahiya naan avvaaru illaamal ivvulahil saivan yenak koorik kolludhal oru siridhum porundhaadhu.
thimidhanilai thandharulaai sivaloaha sundharanae. 30.

Tamil Serials – vaazhkaya yosinga daa, thala ezhutha nalla vaasingadaa… _ Hava Nagila!
Tamil Serials – vaazhkaya yosinga daa, thala ezhutha nalla vaasingadaa…
Endha serial eduthalum ore comedy dhaan po… ennada serial la podhuva azha dhaane seivaanga, iva enna comedy nu solrale… enna achu nu neenga nenekalam. Aana paarunga namma tamil serials la comedy aana matters naraya irukku.
Ella serials layum universala oru penn tyagi. tyaga bhramathin motha uruvam… ellarukkum ellathayum vittukuduthu thanakunu edhuvume vechukanum nu nenechu kooda paakkadha oru character. elarukkum bheeshmar, draupadi nenepu. aana oona oru sabadaham edukkavendiyadhu. andha thuppu ketta sabadhathukku oru illakiya udharanam, oru bayangaramana background music. pathadhunnu BGM la "parithranaya saadhu naam" slokam vera, closeup shots, zoom in, ennalamo fotography techniques.
Cinema kettadhu kedu, serial villi/ villain galodu sarvadesa level planning ku munnala cinema villians lam onnume illa…. murder, karpaazhippu, terrorism, kollai, sothu prachnai edhayaum vidradhu illai. evolo bajaariya thanama irukka mudiyumo avolo bajaari ya iruppanga. correcta thedi pidichu erkanave kalyanam aana ponnai/ payyana love pannuvanga…. sila peroda character suspense laye irukkum… avanga nalla vangala, ketta vangala nu charactera ye purinjukka mudiyadhu
Adhavadhu edho thaangikkalam… aana ella Main hero and heroine ku minumum 3 kalyanam aagidum. oruthiya kalyanam pannanumnu yosippanga aana mudiyadha soozhnilai. avolodu kalayanam pannama oru kuduthanam. innu oruthiku veetula force panni kalayanam panni vechuduvaanga, adhunala avaoloda modhal la pidikama, apram pidichipoi oru kuduthanam. moonavadha, oru ponnuku soozhnilai nala thali katta vendiya kattayam vandhudum. indha kalyanam panna pengalakku, each atleast 2 husbands iruppanga. orutharukku oruthar relateda vera iruppanga. "petrol velai erichu nu crude oil oothunen, crude oil vela erichunu, mannennai oothunen, ippo edhula odumnu ennakkum theriyala, adhukkum theriyala" ipidi karagattakaranla koundamani solvaru. adhu madhiri, yaaru yaaroda purushan/ pondatti nu paakaravangalukkum puriyadhu, nadikkaravangalukkum puriyadhu.
Indha kuzhappam podhadhunu ivangalukku pirandha kuzhandhaigala, mathi mathi vittuduvaanga porandha odene. apram indha kozhandhaingaluku valandha odane each other mela love vandhudum. sollavum mudiyama, sollama irukavum mudiyama thenaruvaanga valatha thay/ thandhai, petha thay/ thandhai, nadulavandha thay/ thandhai.
Idhu pathadhunnu, ella kadhailayum ippo ellam cinema range ku romance, double act, triple act, poorva janmam, ellam sendhu kozhappudhu. meesai vechu oru character, vekkaama inno onnu. thanga mudiyala. ella story layum ippo kaattu lendhu thappichi vara madhiri oru action sequence vera. aa oo na oru police pattalam (nermayana police la vidaradhulla nu sabatham pannirukkanga tamil thirai), goondaism, theeviravaadham, dhideer thirupangal nu izhuthu vittudaraanga. ellathukum nadoola, yaaro oru aal edho diary ya eppovo tholachuruppar. adha theda oru kootam porapadum. thedikitte irukkum bodhu dhideer nu oru naal oru announcement, "ivarukku badhil ivar". takkunu aala mathidaraanga. ellaathukkum mela outdoor shooting vera. imsa thaangaadhu. enga eduthalum ore kuppaya thaane edukkaranga.
Javvu madhiri izhuppanga. oru penn pregnant aana, nejemave pathu maasam aagidum andha serial la avalukku kozhandhai poraka. nejamave kolangal devayani, padhi serial la pregnant aanaaga, avangalukku nejemave kozhandayum porandhuduchu, andha kozhai ku 5 vayasu aagara varaikkum serial thodarum… idhu enna kodumai. seri javvu madhiri izhukaraangale, ippidi thaan irukkum nu nambi 1 month paakama vittuttu apram tv la patha, andha time la vere edho serial varudhu. enna nu ketta, ore vaarathula ellarayum thirithi, padhi charactersa sava adichi, micham irukkara ellarayum sethu nikka vechu "subham" nu pottu mudichuttangalam. 🙂
Idha paathu rasikarthuku oru kootam alayuthu. adhungala ellam thiruthu ppa narayana!!
4 comments on “Tamil Serials – vaazhkaya yosinga daa, thala ezhutha nalla vaasingadaa…”
type casting oru matter miss pannitteenga. oruttan oru serial la thirudana vandhannaella serial layum avan thirudan thaan, ore police officer avana ella serial layum thorattuvan, endha serial la pudhicchuttan, edhula pudikka poran…. ella statsayum correct maintain vera pannuvaanga….. indha kandraviya rasikarthukkune oru gumbal……..
Actually neenga onnu maranthuthinga… ippolam serials la vara songs ku thaan jaasthi rasigar kootam.. Apporam neenga onnu note pannanum that one month kaporam antha serial a parthalum onnum periya progress erukathu…. or antha serial neenga sonna madiri mudinji erukum abruptly

05. Oka Praanam - Kaala Bhairava -

Tamil Kamakathaikal - bus sil avalai ottha kathai
Home » Tamil Kamakathaikal » bus sil avalai ottha kathai
bus sil avalai ottha kathai
vanakkam. yen peyar kiri. selaththilulla pirapala kalloori onril poriyiyal 3aam aandu padikkiren. yen sondha oor sennai. inku roommeduththu thanki padichsittirukken. naan inku solla vandha kathai yenakkum, yenkooda padeekkum yenga sennaiyaichsendha keethaankira pennaiyum patriyadhu. aamaanga, konjam pinnokki povom….
naan intha kaalejla sendha puthusula yeppavumpola reking, aattam paattamnu muthal varudam mudinjiduchchu. yenga dipaartmendla padikkiravankalla naanum, keethaavumthaan sennaiyai senthavarkal. maththavankellaam paathi per ithe oorai senthaveenga, maththaveenga yenkalaip polave veliyoorilirundhu inkavandhu haastalil thanki padippavarkal. ]naanum muthalvarudam viduthiyilathaan thanki padichchen. aanaal anka saappaadu seriyillaadhadhaal thaniyaa maasa vaadakai 800 roopaayukku roomeduththu thaniyaave thankitten.
yenga dipaartmendla irundha penkalla niraiya per azhakaa, soopparaa iruppaaluga. sila ponnuga thookkiya mulaiyudan kaalejjikke sudithaarkkumele kaattittu nadappaaluga. silaper namma kiraamaththu ponnooka maathiri thuppattaavaip pottu yellaaththaiyum moodi marachchittu iruppaaluga.
naan kaalejla intha seenellaam paaththaalum seks aasaikal yenpadhu yen manasila yettaavathu padikkirappave vanthiruchchu. appirundhe seks padam paappathum,kaiyadippathum pazhakikkonden. appirundhe seks patriya arivum valara aarampichsiduchchu. veettil appaavum, ammaavum velaikku poraaveenga, athanaala yeppavum aalirukkamaattaanga. athanaala yeppavoom veettila ammanaththudan seks padampaaththu kaimutti adichsitteyiruppen. athileye oru aanandham. aanaa yenthap pennin rakasiya ankangal yethaiyum paaththathe kidaiyaadhu. aanaa yen nanparkal adikkadi yenkaavathu paaththa seenkalaip paththi solli veruppeththuvaanuga. naanum avanuga kitta, ava mulaiya paaththen, ivakumiyum podhu paaththennu reel viduven. maththapadi yendha seenum paaththathu kidaiyaadhu.
kaalejlayum yendha penkal kittayum vazhinju pesittirukka maatten. ) naanundu, yen velaiyundunu nadanthukkuvathaal kaalejla yenkooda padikkira penkal kitta oru nalla peru yenakku yeppavum undu. andha kaaranaththaaleye pala penkal yenkitta vandhu virumbi pesa aarampichsaangal. naanum avinga kitta vendum podhu pesikkolven. aanaalum kaathal, kaththarikkaa ithellaam kidaiyaadhu. summaa pesippen.
keethaavaippaththi sollanumnaa, amaithiyaana kerakdar. perumpaalum penkalkitta mattumthaan pesuvaal. yendha paiyankittayum vazhinjittu nikkamaattaa. mariyaathaiyaaththaan pesuvaal. athanaaleye avalai rendu pasanga kaathalichsaanga. aanaal aval yaaraiyum kaathalikkalai. aval avinga oorile yaaraiyo kaathalichsittirukkaanu pasankakitta paravichchu. aanaal aval yethaiyum perisaa kandukkalai. maththapadi keethaavaip paththi sollanumnaa, aappil mulaikal, yeppavum thuppattaavaip pottu maraichsitte pokiraval. yaarum paaththirak kootaathunnu thuppattaavai moodimaraichche aniyum nerththi, yellaaraiyum kavarum. metraasai senthavalaai irunthaalum, avalidam kiraamaththu penkalukkirukkum adakkam kaanappattathuthaan periya vishayam. avalin petrorin valarppu appadi. yenga dipaartment kaamaraasakkalin kanavil valam varupavarkalil avaleem oruththi. yenga pasankalin aasaikalil avalin kai, kaallayaavathu vizhundhu ava pundaiyai paaththitanumkirathu yenpathum or aasai. aanaal avalidam appadi neradiyaak ketkarathukku yaarukkum thairiyamillaadhadhaal avalidam pammiye irunthaankal.
naan yeppavum metraaspokum pothum passil pokuvadhe vazhakkam. yenenraal direyinil povathu yenakku pidikkaadhu.
appadi naan passil pokumpodhu kitte aankalo, penkalo yaarvendumaanaalum irukkalaam. naan passil pokirathukku ithuvum or kaaranam. aanaal yenketta neram perumpaalum aankalthaan kitteyiruppaarkal. orurimurai mattumthaan pompalainga vanthirukkaanga. athuvum 50 vayasai thaandiya kezhavikal. oreyoru thadavai 25 vayasupponnu vanthirunthaa. paakka thalathalannu azhakaayirunthaa. aanaa avakootaye ava purushanum vanthirundhaan. athu 3per amarum seettenpathaal, naan jannal oraseettila amara, ava purushan kampiyil saaindhu thoonkavenum yenpatharkaaga ava pondaattiyai naduvila vuttuttu avanandha ora seettil ukkaanthittaan. aven tholmela ottiya maathiri ukkaarave yen sunni yenthirichsuchchu. naan avalin tholmela ottiyamaathiriyirukka avalin udampilirundhu sent manam yennai kirankadiththadhu. aanaalum yethirpaakkira maathiri yethum nadakkalai. aval ava purushan mel saanjittu thoonga, naan paaththitte veruppudan kannayarndhu thoonkitten. naan yevvalavo neram aval yemmela saanjaalnaa yeppadiyaavathu avalin mulaiyaiyaavathu thadavitalaamnu yevvalavo yethirpaaththen. aanaa andha sinna vaaippukooda yenakku kidaikkalai. naanum yekkaththudan kannaadi yoram saaindhu thoonkitten.
ippadi pala vaaippukal yennai vittu nazhuvip poyina. oru velai avalthaan thoonkaraalla, nammaavadhu avaloda mulaiyai thadavalaamnu yenakku yendha oru yosanaiyum yettavillai.
intha sinna nikazhchchiyai ninaichchu palamurai kaiyadichchen. appadiyoru seks piththan naan. “sari, namakku passilellaam, yokam kidaiyaathena, ninaichcha yenakkoo, andha passaalthaan yen muthal seks anupavame nikazhndhadhu. aamaanga…. athuvum andha pasthaan yen muthal sekskku adiththalam pottadhu mattumindri, yenakku mikap periya paadaththaiyum karrukoduththathu…. yenakku andha pas thandha uravai solkiren kelungal.”
orumurai sani, gnaayirudan sernthaapla 5 naalleevu viduramaathiri nilaimai yerpattadhu. kaalejjilayum thinkatkizhamaiye arivichsittaanga. irunthaalum yenakku munnaadiye theriyum. athanaala naan konjanaalukku munnaadiye pas dikket puk pannittu vanthitten. 3 per ukkaarum seettu.
anke yenga kaalej keethaa ninnittirundhaal. avakitta naan athikamaa pesinathu kidaiyaadhu. oriru murai mattum yen thevaikkaaga naanum, ava thevaikalukkaaga avalum pesirukkom. maththapadi yendha oru piranssippum kidaiyaadhu. aval yenkitta “andha seet yennuthu. anka ukkaaranum”
“saari, ulla vaanga” appadinu naan rendu kaalaiyum thookkikka, andha periyavarum kaalai vizhakkikka, aval yethir seettu kampiyai pidichsitte ulle vanthaal. avalin kundi yen kan munnaal mella nakarndhu pokave yen kaama aasaikal uyirpiththana. aanaalum avalin kunam oru murai manathil vandhu pokave, yezhundha aasaikal paduththuk kontadhu.
naanga rendu perum naanga irankum oorkalaip patriyum pesittu, appadiye yenkalin veedukalai patriyum pesikkontom. aval aanaalum konjam saathuvaakaththaan pesinaal. naan yenthavitha kaamavunarchchiyum illaamal avakitta pesittirukka, pas kilambi poittirundhadhu. avakitta pesittirunthathaala yeppa pas kilampichsunu naan kavanikkaveyillai. mani 9yai thaandiyadhu. aval ava veettirku pon panni passil vanthittirukkennu sonnaal. naanum yenga veettirku pon panni vanthittirukkirathai solla yenkaveettil yellaarum santhoshappada pesittu kat panninen. pin konjaneram aval koota pesittirukka mani 10 aayirundhadhu. aval kan sorukum maathiri irukkuthunu thookkittaal. naan konja neram mopailla kem vilaiyaadittu 15 nimidaththil naanum thoonga rediyaaga yenkittirundha perisu kaalai madakki thoonga mudiyaamal yezhundhu nadakkayirundha idaththil thundai virichchu paduththittadhu. avalaip paakka aval madiyil oru pekkai vachchittu nallaa thoonkittirundhaal. yen thol avalin thol mela muttittirundhadhu. aval thuppattaa pottirundhaalum, avalin oramaaga saitil avalin mulaikal sudithaarukkul thenpattadhu. athaippaakka paakka yensunni yezhumba aarampiththathu. aanaal avakitta maattikkondaal kaalej varaikkum peru naaridum. yennathaan payam irunthaalum, kaamaththin mun ithellaam sellumaa? kaamamthaan vendradhu. naan mella yen kaikalai katti ukkaanthukondu, yen itadhu kaiyaal avalin pek oramaaga kaiyai seluththi avalin mulaikitte kondu ponen.
aanaalum yen kaikal nadungina. naan yen kaikalai irukkamaaga kattikka yen kaikalin nadukkam konjam kuraindhadhu. mella kaineetti, yen aatkaatti viralaal avalin sudithaarin mel kai vechchen. naan thodukindra muthal mulai, athuvum ilam mulai. udampenkum karant adichsamaathiri irundhadhu. appadiye viralaal mella aval mulaiyin saitil idikka, aval mulai pansupola irukka, manasenkum payaththudan mella avalin aappil mulaiyin saitil viralaal azhuththa aval yendha unarchchiyumillaamal thoonkittirundhaal. athu yenakku saathakamaaka poga naan moondru viralkalai onnu seththu ava mulaiyin mel sutiyai thadavinen. romba aananthamaaka irukka, naan ava mulaiyin sutiyai thadavittu, mella azhuththinen. avalidamirundhu konjam sinunkal velippada, naan dappena paiyai uruvittu kannai mooditten. rendu nimisham kazhichchu paakkaiyil avalum athe maathirithaan thoonkittirundhaal. vandi konjam vekamaa poittirundhadhu. yenakku meendum payam vara, kidaiththa sukam pothumena naan kannayara aarampiththen. avalum nallaa thoonkinaal. naan konjam kannayarnthiruppen aval yen thol meethu saainthaal. naan vizhiththu avalai paakka, aval nallaa thoonkittirundhaal. avalin amsamaana udhadukal yennai sundiyizhukka, naan avalin mukaththaiye paaththittu, pin avalin thalaiyaipidichchu andha pakkam thiruppi vitten. avalum thirumpikka, naan kannayara aarampikka meendum saainthaal. naan meendum avalai thiruppi vittuttu, avalai vittu konjam nakarndhu ukkaanthitten. mani appave 11kitta aakiyirukka, mella kannayarndhu thoonga aarampiththen. yenga pasla yerinjittirundha sinna laittaiyum nadaththunar anaikka, passenkum kummiruttaanathu. aanaalum kitteyirukkaravangalai mattum thelivaa paaththa theriyum. naan yellaa sinthanaiyum moottai kattittu, thoonga aarampiththen. muthal muraiyaa mulaiyai sudithaarudan thotta santhosham manathenkumirukka thoonginen. nallaa thoonkittirukka yaaro yen thodaiyin meethu kaiyaivechchu varudinathupola unarvu yerpada, naan appadiye irunthen. andha kai yen thodaiyenkum thadaviyadhu. mella yen thodaikalai andha kai varudittu yen sunni kottaikalin melpattadhu. naan kanavena ninaichchittu appadiye irukka, andha kai yen kottaikalai mella varudiyadhu. yenakku udampellaam silirkka, naan asaiyaamalirunthen. andha kai penttodu yen sunniyai pidikka, ithayam padapadarththadhu. yen sunniyai varudiyakaikal mella kottaikalai pidichchu kasakka valiththathu. kanavillaiyena therinju kankalai vizhiththen.

Vanakkam Iyya,
b) Lagnathil - Guru mangala yogam - (guruvum, sevvaiyum sernthu ullathu) - neecha banga raja yoga amaipu
c) Jathagathil - Guru chandra yogam, sasi mangala yogamum ullathu (ulgathil ulla pengalil sirantha pennaga, anaivarukum theriyum prabala nabaraga ulagil vaazhpavar)
d) Laganthai 7aam athipathi paarvai - penmani migavum azhaganavar - Elizabeth azhagirku solla venduma :) :)
e) 6il raagu - neenda aayul + pala sandaigalai paarthavar
f) 2il sukkran - Yogathipathi sukkaran magara lagnathirku - (8aam idathai paarkirar - neenda ayul)
g) 3il neecha budhan - 9aam idathirku neradi paarvai - bagyasthanam strong aaga ullathu - (9aam veetirku guru+budhan paarvai). Neecham petraalum, andha veetin athipathi lagnathil amarndhu neecha bangam petrullar :)
f) 8aam idathirku - Laganthipathi/2aam athipathi(sani)+(sevai)+sukran paarvai ullathu. - Neenda aayuludan ullar.
g) astamathipathi suryan ucham + Thanthaiku uriya graham aanathal - thanthai moolamaga arasu aalum urimaium kidaithathu
Kalathira dhosam irundhum, atipatu ponathu. Sevai yin 7/8aam parvai - 7 aam idathirku ullathu+ 8aam idathirku ullathu - Lagnathil ulla guruvin parvaiyum 7aam idathirku+ sevaium guruvum sernthu ullathal + sevaiyai sani than 3aam paarvaiyinal lagnathayum, lagnathil ulla guru/sevaiyayum than katupaatil veithu ullar.
Chandranai lagna maaga eduthu kondal, Kataga lagnathirku sevai yogakaragan. chandra lagnathirku 7il amarntha sevai, yogathai kuduthaane thavira sothanai tharavillai :)

Azhakiya Ravanan (1996) : Vennilaa chandana kinnam Song Lyrics

thevidiya family 3
(thupaayil thurairaajan–irandaam pakuthikkuk keezhe kammentsilum yenakku neraaga ee-meyililum pala vaasakarkal irandaam pakuthiyaith thodarndhu oru moonraam pakuthi vendumendru yezhuthiyirukkireerkal. ungal karuththukalukku mathippuk koduththu, itho…)
vithyaakitta yethaiyum maraikkalai- medhuvaa yen veyid potaama okkaandhu avala oththappuram thenamum ava naaththanaar kettukittaankalennu avangalai vekamaa okkarathaippaththich sonnen. ‘aamaam raaja, onakkum thaan oru vadikaal venumilla? aanaa, gyaapakaththula vachsikko, namma rendu kuzhanthaikalum porandhu avanum avalum yen mulaikalla paalkudikkachcha, athukku eedukatta neethaan yenakkup paalkudukkanum, pundaivazhiyaavum thondaivazhiyaavum ooththanum. appa intha naaththanaarai moottaikatti anuppiduven, aamaam.”
ivangalai inka vittuttu naamba konjam neelaa pakkam thirumpuvomaa? oru sinna ஃப்ளாஷ்பேக். neelaave sollattume:
suntharesan (‘sunthar’) yenkammaavoda thankai mavan – yenakku thaai vazhila thambi, oru rendumoonu maasam sinnavan. sinna vayasule irundhe yengalukkulla oru ithu. yellaam ore oor – athanaala yeppavum rendu perum serndhu thirivom, velaiyaaduvom. naanga teens reech aakarachcha thotai naduvul paakkarathum, thodarathum, thadavarathum, nakkarathum, sapparathumnu oru puthu indarest. yenakku maar medittu koothila poonaimayir valaraththotanga avanukku pool nikkath thodanga yenga velaiyaattu veramaathiri thirumpiththu.
(ithukkumela inka yezhuthakkoodaadhu – rendu perume mainarkal. oru naalanji varusham aasaiyum vaaippum irukkavanga yeppadiyellaam irunthiruppomnu neenkale karpanai seithukkunga. muthal thadavai muzhusaa senjappuram panjum neruppum pakkaththula pakkaththula irunthaa paththiyeriyarathu iyarkaithaanennu rendu veettulayum kandukkaama vittuttaanga. yenkammaa mattum kaandom upayokikarathap paththi pothuppadaiyaa solla, ippa sunthar thevaiyaana alavu kaandom staak vachsirukkaan. puthu praandu yethaavathu vanthaa mothalla vaankarathu avanthaan.)
rendu perum ippa kaalejla senthuttom. plas doo mudinjappave yenkappaa ammaakitta naanga kalyaanam seithukka aasaippadurathaach sonnom. “akkaa-thambi muraiyila athu mudiyaadhu, andha aasaiya maranthudunkannu rendu veettulayum sollittaanga. appathaan yenga roomkallaye okka aarampichsom. ‘veettula thittuvaanga, naanga sandai pottukittu odippoyi vadakka yenkayaavathu yenga oravumuraiyak kaattikkaama kalyaanam seithukkarathu’nnu thittam, aanaa yaarum moochsuvitallaiye. haallaye yellaar yethurlayum oththirunthaakkooda onnum solliyirukka maattaankapola.
suntharukku sennaiyila pet roliyam deknaalaji korsla atmishan kaartu vanthathu. anju varusham kors. thookkikittu yenkitta odi vandhaan. “sunthar, itha nee yenakkaaga vidakkoodaadhu. Once in a lifetime chance. poi udane jaayin pannidu. yenakkaaga mis pannaa yenakkum yeppothum oru kutra unarchi irukkum. neeyum orunaal illennaa orunaal ivalaala oru nalla vaazhkkaiya izhnthuttamennu varuththappaduve. kors mudinji varachcha yenakkuk kalyaanam aakalainnaa naam veliyur illa, velinaattukke poyi kattikkalaam. illennaa naamba kalyaanam seithukkara kanavai moottaikatti vachsiduvom. nee inka varumpothellaam yen pundaiyai unakkuth tharuven.”
thupaayilerundhu yenga otavukkaarar thurairaajan leevula vanthappo avarukkum yenakkum kalyaanam senjivachchi yenna avaroda avanga oorukku verattittaanga. naan nallaa olvaangina ponnunnu ஃபர்ஸ்ட்நைட்டுல theriyaamayaa irukkum? yen maamiyaarukku yennaiyum suntharaiyum paththi nallaave theriyum. yellaam otavuthaane? aanaa avanga kavalaip pattathaave theriyalai. “avanum thupaai porathukku munna sila penkalai anupavichsirukkaan. ithallaam intha naalla sakajamthaane?” appadinnu yenakku thairiyam solli ulla anuppichsaanga.
leevu mudinja kaiyoda yen kanavaroda thupaai ponappuram moonu varusham jaaliyaap poyidichchi. thevaikkumelaye sampalam. dipaartment vandi, diraivar. savukariyamaana apaartmenat. neraiya ஃப்ரெண்ட்ஸ். ivaroda ishtappadi lootti. seekkirame innum yendha jodiyaiyaavathu oru veraittikkaaga yenga seksla seththukkanumnu nenaichchen paarunga, appa theettu ninnupochchi. naan karppamnu dest risaltu sonnathula irundhe yennai paththiramaap paaththukkaraar. muthal moonumaasam karu apset aakak kootaathunnu jendilaa treet panraar. okkarathukooda nithaanamaavethaan nadakkuthu. aduththa moonumaasam yevvalavu joraa mudiyumo avvalavu joraa oththuth thallarom.
aaraam maasak kadaisila yennai oorukku azhaichsittup poyi avanga ammaakitta oppadaich si “avanga kiraamaththula nalla aaspaththiri illai. namma naakaila aaspaththirila pirasavam paaththukkanga. avasaramnaa pakkaththila thiruvaaloorla periya aaspaththirikkup pokalaam. paththiram. pirasavam aayi oru maasamo rendu maasamo mudinjathum neenga yaaraavadhu azhaichsikittuvandhu yenkitta seththudunga”-nnu oppadaichchittu vanthutaraar.
appa pet roliyam deknaalaji korsla raank vaankikittu sunthar inka varaan. thupaayila oru periya aayil kampanila selakt aayirukkaanaam. yunivarsidilerundhu dikiri சர்டிஃபிகேட் kedaichsathum pokanum. paasport, vark parmid, resitans parmid (visaa) yellaam vaanga naakappattinaththula yejandu irukkarathaala inka vanthirukkaan. sollanumaa, vandha naalla irundhu naanga rendu perum oththukittirukkom. yen maamiyaar atha yenkarej panraanga, pundaivazhiyaa kuzhanthai sulapamaa veliya varanumnaa thenamum oththu andha koothiottai thorandhu irukkaappala paaththukkanumnu yellaarum namparaanga.
aanaa, munthi irundha vekaththoda okkakkoodaadhu, karu kalainjitak kootaathunnu koothikku yethirla veliya ukkaandhu meloda okkavendiyirukku. paavam, avan appadi oththappuram, avan sunniya yen vaayila vaankikittu kanji kazhalra varaikkum oomparen. itho naal nerunkidichchi. vali kandathum aaspaththirila seththutaraanga. naarmal delivari. moonarai kilo yetai, kyoottaa oru aankuzhanthai. raajaavai urichsivachsirukku. kuzhanthai avan appaakitta porathukku munna inthak kathai raajaakitta povuthu.
annikki, thethikkanakku pottu yethirpaarththapadi, yen maamanaar ponla “neelaavukku aankuzhanthai poranthirukku, thaayum seyum nalam”-nnu sonnaaru. “ippa leevu kedaikkaathu maamaa. inka romba pisi. rendu maasam vachsirundhu yellaa velaiyum seiyara alavukku otampu therinappuram inka azhachsikittu vaanga”-nnu sollittu vithyaakitta vivaraththaich sonnen. neelaavum kozhanthaiyum vanthuttaa yenga rileshanship yenna aarathu?
“athukku ippave yen kavalaippatanum, raaja? yethaavathu oru vazhi kidaikkum, paaru. illennaa mella neelaakkaavai vazhikkuk konduvandhu ava oru naal, naan oru naalnu unnaip panku pottukkittaap pochchi. yaar kantadhu, ore kattilla naanga renduperume ore neraththula on vaaikkum sunnikkum velai kuduththaalum nee thaankuva raaja!” intha vithyaavukku yethuvume praaplamillai. appadi eesiyaa yeduththukkaravangalukku aduththu nadakkapporathukooda innum eesiyaa aakkumaam. pinna paarungalen. ava delivari aaki paththu naal aaspaththirila irukkachsaye inke irundha andha naaththanaaroda maamiyaar poyittaankannu oru pon vanthathu. purushanodu serndhu maamiyaar kaariyamellaam seiyanumnu andha naaththanaar avasaramaa oorukkup porappattup poyittaanga.
athuvaavathu innikki illennaa innoru naal thirumpitaththaan poranga. aanaa yethipaarkkaama, inka vithyaavoda kanavan kampani velaiyaa vera oru aapeesukku kampani kaarla ponapodhu yethirla vandha pet rol trak onnu mothi, andha yedaththulaye kaar yerinjipochchi. avanga metal ID tag, official movement log-book at the company itha vachchi kampaniyila koota velai seiyaravankale confirmation of death yerpaadu senjittaanga. intha co-incidence kathaikalla vara maathiri irukkalaam, aanaa appadi yeppavaavathu nijavaazhkkaiyilayum nadanthuduthu illaiyaa? kathaikale nijavaazhkkaiyin pirathipalippukal thaane? kaikkuzhanthaikaloda vithya vithavaiyaa than apaartmenttukkuth thirumpinaa.
‘raaja, intha oru maasam nee leevu pottuttu un kozhanthaikalaiyum yennaiyum paaththukkadaa. appuram naan unnaip paaththukkaren. ippakooda naan kozhanthaikalukkup paal oottikitte unnai oompip paalkudikkarendaa. athanaala unakku seks illayennu kavalai irukkaathu.” ippa yen aapeesla sampalamillaadha leevu pottuttu moonuperaiyum naan paaththukkaren. appa yethirpaarkkaama oru ee-meyil. neelaa yezhuthiyirukkaa. yen lep-daappa konjanaalaa intha apaartmendulathaan vachsirukken. itho andha eemeyil:
“itha yeppadi ponla solrathunnu theriyalai. konjam deliket mettar. athanaala eemeyilla yezhutharen. yenga siththi makan, athaavathu thaayaar vazhiyila thambi muraiyaavuthu, suntharnu per. andha sunthar rendumoonu maasamaa inka yenga voottulathaan thupaaikku varathukku paasport, vork parmid, visaa yellaam vaankarathukkaaga thangiyirukkaan. yenga ammaa sonnaanga, ‘karppamaayirukkachcha rekularaa oththukittu irukkanum neelaa, appathaan vazhi adaichsikkaama irukkum, delivari eesiyaa irukkum. athaan yen thankachchi pillai sunthar inka irukkaan illa, avanaiye oththukkalaame. nallapaiyan, paakkavum raaja maathiri irukkaan, kadaisi kadaisila vayiththumel veyid potaama, lesaa nozhachchi yedutaannaa athaiyum porumaiyaa seivaan.’ seithaan.
paavam, thanakku thirupthiyillaama ippadi yenakkaaga paadupatarathap paaththu manasu thaankaama, athu neenkannu nenaichchi avana oompip paalkudippen, yenakku namma pildinkla vera sila apaartmentsulerundhu yen ஃப்ரெண்ட்ஸ் neenk ippa namma pakkaththu apaartmendula oru kalyaanamaana oriyaa ponna, vithyaannu per sonnaanga, ava kanavanukkuth therinche oththukittirukkeenkannum ava ippa rettaikuzhanthai undaai irukkaannum athukku neengadhaan nija appaannum ponla sonnaanga. appa naan sundhara oththukkarathum thappillainnu thonichchi. neenga purinjippeenga.
avan petroleum technology padichchi, yunivarcidi renk vaangi, kempas intarvyoola nallaa seithathunaala udane thupaaila oru maldineshanal aayil kampanila velai pottuk koduththuttaanga. avanukku oru appaartmendum laank leesla yeduththuk kodukkaraankalaam. neenga namma pildinklaye oru apaartment yerpaadu seithaa athaiye suntharukku yeduththukkalaam. appa neenga, naan, sunthar andha vithya naaluperume oththumaiyaa irunthukkalaamnu naan ninaikkiren. unka moonu kozhanthaiyume ungaloda iruppaanga. . naan solrathu puriyumnu ninaikkiren.”
adeyappaa, iva plaanninkla vithyaavaiye peet pannittaale! inth ee-meyila appadiye vithyaavukkup padichsikkaattinen. ‘
“aamaa, inka naamba seitha maathiri anka avunga, niyaayamthaane? pesaama naan irukka intha apaartmendaiye lees yeduththukkach sollu. yenakku andha trak kampenilayirundhu kaampanseshannu heviyaa oru thokaikku sek vanthirukku. atha vachchi unka apaartmentai neenga lees yeduththukkalaam. konja naalaikkappuram naan suntharaiye sivil merej senjikkittaa yaarum onnum sollamudiyaadhu illa? yenakku ivar velai seitha kampeni oru nalla amavunt maasaamaasam penshanaa varum. athanaala panam oru pirachnaiye illai.”
yellaam plaanpadi kaalak kiramaththula nadanthuthunga. vithyaavak kattikka yaarukkuk kasakkum? yenna rendu kozhanthai irukku. athukkupathil than pondaattikku therinche innoru koothi, athuvum akkaavoda koothi, okkak kedaikkuthe! ippallaam inka yaar kanavan yaarunnu kanakku kidaiyaadhu. anekamaa yellaarum ore kattillathaan paduppom. yeppadi venaalum majaaseivom. yaar mulaiyila yenthak kuzhanthai paal kudikkuthunnum kanakke illai. yenthak kuzhanthai venaalum yendha ammaa mulaila venaalum paal kudikkuthu. michsam irukka oru mulaila naano suntharo paal kudichsikittiruppom. paal kudikkaadha kanavan yethuvaavathu oru koothila oththukittiruppaan. paal kudikkara kanavan sunniya yevalaavathu kaiyadichsikittu iruppaa.
keliyum kindalumaa லைஃப் jaaliyaa povuthu. rendu perukkum paathi naal vevveru ஷிஃப்ட்ல tyoodi varum. athanaala rendu manaivikalukkum moonu kuzhanthaikalukkum yaaraavadhu oruththar iruppom. oru naal sunthar kitta”yen thambi, unakkunnu oru kuzhanthai venaamaa? athanaala konja kaalam unka athikaara poorvamaana manaivi vithyaavai neenga mattum okkalaamillaiyaa? yenru ketten. “anne, appadippaaththaa vithyaavukkup porandha rendu kozhanthaikalukkum sattappadi naan thaan thanthai. athanaal ungalukku thaan oru nampar kuraiyuthu. vidunga anne. naamba paattukku viththiyaasamillaama okkalaam. yaarukkuk karu pidichsaalum athuvum namma kuzhanthai. sattappadi yaarthunnu sonnaa athappaththi namakkenna? லைஃப் ippadiye odinaa majaathaan.”
Ava Purusan Nallaa Ongi Ongi Kuttha, Saavitri Ennaiyee Paatthaal

I was scared to see this movie in the beginning because, chumma manasai pottu kuzhapikka vaendamnu thaan. Aerkanavae US la, "Law and Order: Criminal Intent" paarthuttu theruvula poravanga varavangalai ellam paarthu santhaegam varuthu. Irunthaalum antha padathula apadi enna thaan irukkunnu voru curiosity. Athey maathiri cleaning lady, maintenance guy apadinnu veettu keya copy panni kodukarathula enakku vudan paadu illai.
Intha padam ellarukkum voru nalla paadam. Kandippa ellarum paarka vaendiya padam.

Summa solla koodathu, padam attagaasamana thriller. Kadaisi varaikkum paey padama illai Psycho storyaannu theriyama kondu poraanga. Ithu ellathukum maela, aen intha kolai ellam nadakathu, yaar ithai ellam seira apadinnu konjam kooda yugikka mudiyella. It keeps you at the edge of your seat.
"Rishi", ithu namma hero.Engaeyo paartha mugamnu paartha, namma tamilla "Richard" apadingara paerla vanthavaru, Shaliniyoda annan. Nalla nadichirukaaru.

raal·p paarlad (Ralph Parelette) enpavar pirapala amerikkap paechchaalar. oru murai avar ‘vithi’ parrip paecha oru kannaadi jadiyudan maedaikku vanthaar. antha jadiyil chiriya peens vithaikalum periya vaathumaik koddaikalum (Walmuts) irunthana. jadiyai oru murai nanraakak kulukki viddu ankirunthavarkalukku athaik kaanpiththaar. alavil periya vaathumaik koddaikal jadiyin maelpuraththilum, chiriya peens vithaikal adippakuthiyilum irunthana. “nanparkalae!inthap peens vithaikalil onru … Continue reading "naamae nam vithiyaith theermaaneththuk kolkirom"
raal·p paarlad (Ralph Parelette) enpavar pirapala amerikkap paechchaalar. oru murai avar ‘vithi’ parrip paecha oru kannaadi jadiyudan maedaikku vanthaar.
antha jadiyil chiriya peens vithaikalum periya vaathumaik koddaikalum (Walmuts) irunthana. jadiyai oru murai nanraakak kulukki viddu ankirunthavarkalukku athaik kaanpiththaar. alavil periya vaathumaik koddaikal jadiyin maelpuraththilum, chiriya peens vithaikal adippakuthiyilum irunthana.
“nanparkalae!inthap peens vithaikalil onru ennedam uthavi kaedkinrathu. atharkum vaathumaik koddaikalukku inaiyaaka maelae thanka aachaiyaam, naan atharku uthavap poakiraen. unkal munnelaiyilaeyae antha chiriya peensai maelae vaikkiraen paarunkal. aahaa, ippoathu peens vithaikkuth thaan eththanai chanthosham”
avar marupadi jadiyai nanraakak kulukkinaar. “adadaa, kulukkalil peens vithai than palaiya idaththirkae poay viddathae! antha peens vithaikku mikavum varuththam. chamaththuvam enpathu illaiyae enru ankalaayppu. athu marupadi ennedam vaendik kolkirathu. thaan maelae poayth thankaa viddaalum paravaayillai. vaathumaik koddai thanakkuch chamamaakak keelae thanka vaendum enkirathu”
“chari, athaiyum cheyvomae. paarunkal. unkal munnelaiyil vaathumaik koddai onrai eduththu peenskalukku adiyil vaikkiraen. chari thaanae!”
avar marupadi jadiyai nanraakak kulukkinaar. munpu poalavae antha vaathumaik koddai maelae vanthu viddathu. peens adiyil thanki viddathu.
“nanparkalae ithu iyarkaiyin neyathi. alavil chiriyavai keelum, alavil periyavai maelum eppoathum thankum. peens maelae vara vaendumaanaal atharku orae vali, athu alavil perithaaka valarvathu thaan. athai viddu naam eththanai thaan uthavinaalum kaalaththin kulukkalil ellaamae thankalukku uriya idaththilaeyae thanka naeridum.”
“nanparkalae peenskkum vaathumaik koddaikkum thankalin aachaippadi thankalai maarrik kolla mudiyaathu. aanaal manetharkalaip poaruththavarai naam appadik kaiyaalaakaathavarkal alla. kadavul nammai appadip padaikkavillai. naam uyara vaendumaanaal valara vaendum. atharkaana muyarchikalai edukka vaendum. appadi muyarchi eduppathan moolamaakavo, muyarchi edukka maruppathan moolamaakavo naamae nam vithiyaith theermaaneththuk kolkirom” enru koori mudiththaar.
ithu oru mika alakaana uvamai. raal·p paarladdin peensaip poal thaan nammil palarum irukkirom. yaaraavathu aethaavathu cheythu eppadiyaavathu nammai oru nalla nelaikkuk kondu poay vidak kaaththu irukkirom.
appadi verumanae kaaththuk kidakkira kaalaththil paathiyaich chariyaaka, puththichaaliththanamaaka, mulumanathodu payanpaduththinaal poathum, antha nelaikkuth thaevaiyaana chakala thakuthikalaiyum nam muyarchiyaal naamae uruvaakkik kolla mudiyum. yaar thayavum inri nam ilakkukalai naamae chenradaiya mudiyum. maaraaka nalla naeraththirkaakavo, aduththavar uthavikkaakavo, athishdaththirkaakavo kaaththuk kidappavarkal irukkumidaththilaeyae irukka vaendi varum. athu thaan vithi.
enavae arivaiyum thakuthikalaiyum valarththuk kollunkal. kaalaththirkaerpa thiramaiyaaka, viraivaakach cheyalpadunkal. unkal arivum thiramaiyum athikappada athikappada unkal ilakkirkaana valikal thaamaakavae thelivaakap pulappadath thuvankum. sareyana chantharppankal thaanaaka unkalaith thaedi vara aarampikkum. ithuvae iyarkaiyin neyathi.

Pakka. Ipadiyum oru heroine ku uru kodukalam nu yosicha Director Nalan, welcome to tamizh cinema ulagam. Thiraikathai otathula knjm thadumaatram irunthalum, Kadathuvatharku vagutha 5 vithigal, Nambikkai Kannan, Nearmayana arasiyal vaathi, psycho inspector, maaya kathanayagi, kidnapping, illa kednapping nu niraya paratum vishayangal padathula. Santhosh oda ela BGM, 4 vari paadalgal super. Padathoda baanila solanum na, ithukku kuruttuthanamana muttal thanamum, murattu thanamana puthisaalithanamum venum.

maṉam eṉbadu ātma-sorūpattil uḷḷa ōr atiśaya śakti. adu sakala niṉaivugaḷaiyum tōṯṟuvikkiṉḏṟadu. niṉaivugaḷai y-ellām nīkki-p pārkkiṉḏṟa-pōdu, taṉi-y-āy maṉam eṉḏṟu ōr poruḷ illai; āhaiyāl niṉaivē maṉadiṉ sorūpam.
maṉadil tōṉḏṟum niṉaivugaḷ ellāvaṯṟiṟkum nāṉ-eṉṉum niṉaivē mudal niṉaivu. idu eṙunda piṟahē ēṉaiya niṉaivugaḷ eṙugiṉḏṟaṉa. taṉmai tōṉḏṟiya piṟahē muṉṉilai paḍarkkaigaḷ tōṉḏṟugiṉḏṟaṉa; taṉmai y-iṉḏṟi muṉṉilai paḍarkkaigaḷ irā.
Padacchēdam (word-separation): uruvam tāṉ āyiṉ, ulahu param aṯṟu ām; uruvam tāṉ aṉḏṟēl, uvaṯṟiṉ uruvattai kaṇ uṟudal yāvaṉ? evaṉ? kaṇ alāl kāṭci uṇḍō? kaṇ adu tāṉ antam-ilā kaṇ.
niṉaivugaḷai-t tavirttu jagam eṉḏṟu ōr poruḷ aṉṉiyam-āy illai. tūkkattil niṉaivugaḷ illai, jagamum illai; jāgra-soppaṉaṅgaḷil niṉaivugaḷ uḷa, jagamum uṇḍu. silandi-p-pūcci eppaḍi-t taṉ-ṉ-iḍam-irundu veḷiyil nūlai nūṯṟu maṟupaḍiyum taṉṉuḷ iṙuttu-k-koḷḷugiṟadō, appaḍiyē maṉamum taṉ-ṉ-iḍattil-irundu jagattai-t tōṯṟuvittu maṟupaḍiyum taṉṉiḍamē oḍukki-k-koḷḷugiṟadu. maṉam ātma-sorūpattiṉiṉḏṟu veḷippaḍum-pōdu jagam tōṉḏṟum. āhaiyāl, jagam tōṉḏṟum-pōdu sorūpam tōṉḏṟādu; sorūpam tōṉḏṟum (pirakāśikkum) pōdu jagam tōṉḏṟādu.
Padacchēdam (word-separation): taṉmai uṇḍēl, muṉṉilai paḍarkkaigaḷ tām uḷa-v-ām. taṉmaiyiṉ uṇmaiyai tāṉ āyndu taṉmai aṟiṉ, muṉṉilai paḍarkkai muḍivu uṯṟu, oṉḏṟāy oḷirum taṉmaiyē taṉ nilaimai tāṉ.
Padacchēdam (word-separation): maṉattiṉ uruvai maṟavādu usāva, maṉam eṉa oṉḏṟu ilai. mārggam nēr ārkkum idu.
ennūlilum mukti y-aḍaivadaṟku maṉattai y-aḍakka vēṇḍum-eṉḏṟu solla-p-paṭ ṭuḷḷapaḍiyāl, maṉōnigrahamē nūlgaḷiṉ muḍivāṉa karuttu eṉ ḏṟaṟindu-goṇḍa piṉbu nūlgaḷai y-aḷaviṉḏṟi-p paḍi-p-padāl payaṉ-illai. maṉattai y-aḍakkuvadaṟku-t taṉṉai yār eṉḏṟu vicārikka vēṇḍum-ē y-allāmal eppaḍi nūlgaḷil vicārippadu? taṉṉai-t taṉṉuḍaiya ñāṉa-k-kaṇṇāl-tāṉ-ē y-aṟiya vēṇḍum. rāmaṉ taṉṉai rāmaṉ-eṉḏṟaṟiya-k kaṇṇāḍi vēṇḍum-ā? ‘tāṉ’ pañca kōśaṅgaḷukkuḷ ḷ-iruppadu; nūlgaḷ-ō avaṯṟiṟku veḷiyil iruppavai. āhaiyāl, pañca kōśaṅgaḷai-y-um nīkki vicārikka vēṇḍiya taṉṉai nūlgaḷil vicārippadu vīṇē. bandhattil irukkum tāṉ yār eṉḏṟu vicārittu taṉ yathārtha sorūpattai-t terindu-koḷvadē mukti. sadā-kālam-um maṉattai ātmāvil vaittiruppadaṟku-t tāṉ ‘ātma-vicāram’ eṉḏṟu peyar; dhiyāṉam-ō taṉṉai saccidāṉanda birahmmamāha bhāvippadu. kaṯṟavai y-aṉaittaiyum oru-kālattil maṟakka vēṇḍi-varum.
Padacchēdam (word-separation): nāṉā vidamāṉa nāma rūpaṅgaḷōḍu tāṉē ulahā samaivadu alāl, tāṉ ōr nimittaṉā attai nirumittu aḷittu samittal purivāṉ alaṉ.

Oru Kodiyil 3 Malargal Tamil Sex Stories in Thanglish Part 35
Oru Kodiyil 3 Malargal Tamil Sex Story in Thanglish Part 34
Naan kattilil eri patuththu kaalkalai thongavittuk kontu sindhuvai en mel izhuththen. Sindhu, “ennataa pannap pore,” endraal. Avalukku muththam ondrai padhilaaka thandhuvittu en poolai aval puntaikkul nuzhaiththen. Sindhu en poolai than puntaiyil ulvaangik kontu en mel patuththirundhaal. “ippa avarai un pinnaale varach chollu,” endru en kaalkalai viriththuk konten.
‘Ennataa…ore neraththile rentu perumaa?” ena sindhu aachchariyaththutan ketka naan aval udhattai en vaayil kavvi suvaiththen. Sindhuvin kanavar sandhoshamaaka aval pinnaal vandhaar. Naan sindhuvin kuntik kolangalai iru kaikalilum patrik kontu aval sooththai virikka, avar than siriya kunjai aval sooththukkul thinikka adhu konjam siramaththutan aval sooththukkul nuzhaindhu kontadhu.
Sindhuvin mukam vedhanaiyil sulikka naan aval udhatukalaik kavvi aval mukaththaik kaiyil pitiththuk kontu aval vedhanaiyai kuraiththen. Sindhuvin kanavar medhuvaaka aval sooththil than kunjai vittu aatta thotanginaar. Ippodhu sindhuvin sooththu ottai virindhu avarutaiya kunju sulapamaaka sendru vandhadhu. Sindhuvukkum vedhanai kuraindhirukka ventum. Aval enakku muththangalaakath thandhu kontirundhaal. Sindhuvin kanavar mukaththil edho mutiyaadhadhai saadhiththuvitta thirupdhi.
Naan en kuntiyai thookki medhuvaaka aval puntaiyil itiththuk kontirundhen. Sindhu maththalam pol irupakkamum iti vaangik kontirundhaal. Sindhuvin kanavar mukam pona pokkil irundhu avarukku avar kunju vetikka thayaaraakivittadhu enpadhaip purindhu konten. Avar kaikaalkal viraikka ssss…ssss…ena paampu pola seerik kontirundhaar. Siridhu neraththil paap ena saththadhutan avar kunju aval sooththil irundhu veli vandhadhu.
Aththutan sindhuvin sooththu ottai surungi viriya adhil irundhu aval kanavarin vindhu vazhiya thotangiyadhu. Naan sindhuvai en mel irundhu thallivittu ezhundhu kattilin vilimpil nindren. Sindhuvai kuppurap pottu aval ituppai pitiththu thookki avalai kaalai viriththu mantiyittu amara seydhen. Aval than kuntiyai uyarththik kontu than thalaiyai pettil saaiththirundhaal. Naan medhuvaaka aval sooththu ottaiyil viralai nuzhaiththen.
Aval utane payandhu, “un kunjai en sooththile vitturaadhetaa, naan seththuruven,” endraal. Sariyena koorivittu en kunjai pin pakkam uppiyirundha aval puntaikkul thiniththen. Aval sooththil en viralai thiruppik konte aval puntaiyil en poolai aatta aarampiththen. Naan seyvadhai aval rasippadhu aval mukaththil piradhipaliththadhu. Avvappodhu punmuruvalutan ennai thirumpip paarththu anupaviththaal. Naan en viralai sooththil irundhu etuththu vittu en kunjaiyum aval puntaiyil irundhu uruvinen. Aval sooththu ottaikku nere en poolin thalaiyai vaikka aval mukaththil kili paraviyadhu.
“shivaa….no…no….”ena aval kadhara, en poolai kannimaikkum neraththil aval sooththil sorukinen. Aval shivaa….ena alarinaal. Aval kangalil irundhu kanneer maalaiyaakak kottiyadhu. En pool aval kuntikkul kachchidhamaaka pukundhu kontadhu. Aval kaikaal en poolai irukkamaakap pitiththuk kontana. Keezh udhattai parkalaal irukak katiththuk kontirundhaal. Siridhu neram appatiye patuththuk kitandhaal.
Naanum endha asaivum kotukkaamal en poolai aval kuntikkulleye niruththi vaiththirundhen. Siridhu neraththil aval sakaja nilaikku thirumpa naan medhuvaaka avalai kuntiyil okka aarampiththen. Ovvoru murai en pool ulle sendru varum podhum aval vedhanaiyil thutippadhu purindhadhu. Eninum aval enakkaaka than vedhanaiyaip poruththuk kontu than kuntiyaik kaattik kontirundhaal. Aval nilaiyaip paarkka enakku paridhaapamaaka irundhadhu. Adharku melum avalai imsikka en manam oppavillai. En poolai aval kuntiyil irundhu uruvinen. Adhu asingaththutan veli vandhadhu. Etuththa vekaththil adhai aval puntaikkul sorukinen.
Sindhuvai naalu kaalil niruththi aval ituppaip pitiththuk kontu en sakdhi muzhuvadhaiyum pirayokiththu aval puntaiyil en thaakkudhalai thotarndhen. Sindhuvin alaral saththamum munakal saththamum andha arai muzhuvadhum edhiroliththadhu. Paththu nimitam varai en thaakkudhalai thotarndha naan unarchchiyin uchchak kattaththai ataindhen. En kottaikal thatikka en poolai aval puntaiyai kizhiththuvituvadhu pol aazhamaaka soruki appatiye niruththik konten.
En kaikal aval ituppai irukap pitiththu en thotaiyutan otta vaiththuk kontadhu. Enakku utal muzhuvadhum 10000 volt minsaaram paaindhadhu pondru adhirndhadhu. En poolil irundhu thuppaakkith thottaa pondru veli vandha vindhu thulikal aval karppap paiyai neratiyaaka thaakkiyadhu. Sindhu appatiye sariya naanum aval mel sarindhen. En pool aval puntaiyil irundhu velivara aval puntaiyil irundhu naan paaichchiya vindhu piravaakamaaka kotti pettai nanaiththadhu.
Sindhu kattilil kitakka naan aval mel patuththirundhen. Iruvarum mikundha kalaipputan irundhom. Naan aval parandha mudhukil mudhdhmittu en sandhoshaththai velip patuththinen. Aval kankal mootiyirukka aval mukaththil melliya punsirippu thenpattadhu. Aval kanavar arukil patuththuk kontu aval vaayil muththamita sindhuvum sandhoshamaaka “i love you darling,” ena koori avarutaiya udhatukalaik kavvik kontaal. Irudhiyil naanum adhil kalandhu kolla siridhu neram engalukkul muththap pottiye natandhadhu. Iravu muzhuvadhum thoongaamal silmishangal seydhu konteyirundhom. Naan melum irantu murai aval puntaiyil en thiramaiyaik kaatta adhai aval kanavar adhisayamaakap paarththu rasiththaar.
Atuththu irundha naatkal muzhuvadhum avarkalutane kazhindhadhu. Sindhuvai naangal vidhavidhamaaka oththom. Sindhuvin kanavar raamukkum parama thirupdhi. Andru iravu naankal anaivarum pesik kontirundhom. Appodhu sindhu, “unga annikku appuram ennataa aachchu. Annan kopappattaaraa?” endraal.
“annan payangaramaa kopappattaar.”
“aiyaiyo appuram eppatitaa avarai samaalichche?”
“anniyai avar munnaale vachchu oththudhaan,” ena naan savakaasamaakach cholla sindhuvin vizhikal virindhadhu.
“aamaa adhu mattumille, ammaavum engalota serndhukkittaanga,” endradhum aval mayangi vizhaadha kuraidhaan.
Appuram anaivarum siridhu neram pesik kontirundhom. Appodhu sindhuvin kanavar edho solla varuvadhum pinnar thayanguvadhumaaka irundhaar.
“ennannaa, summaa sollunga,” endren.
“ille. Naangalum unga femiliyota kalandhukkalaamaa” ena thayangi thayangik kettaar.
“yoo meen kroop seks,” ena naan vinava avar punnakaiyutan thalaiyasaiththaar.
“neenga annan ellaam ore vev lenndhla thaan irukkeenga. Adhanaale annanum anniyum idhukku oththukkuvaangannu ninaikkiren. Appuram pesittu solren,” ena koori naan angirundhu purappatten.
“seekkiram nalla sedhiyota vaanga,” ena avarum sindhuvum en kaiyai kulukka avarkalitamirundhu vitai petren. •Mutrum•
Pinnurai: Indha kadhaikku vaasakarkal aliththa varaverpukku mikavum nandri. Ennutaiya velaip palu kaaranamaaka utanukkutan atuththatuththa paakangalai ennaal thotarchchiyaaka anuppa iyalavillai. Mannikkavum. Idhan atuththa paakam thotarvadhaa ventaamaa enepadhu patri innum mutivu seyyavillai. Adharku mun enakku konjam oivu thevaippatukiradhu.
