Maalai Aaka, Ammavum, Appavum Vara Iyalpaa Irukkira Maathiri Kaaddikkondu, Saappiddellaam Mudichu Room Poyi Thoonga Ninaikkaiyil Thookkam Varalai. Ped Laid Poddu Vidduddu Eekkatthil Mopail Moolamaaka Tamilderddiyil KaamaKadhaikalai Padikka Aarampittheen. Athil Thivyaa Ennum Kathaapaatthiratthil, Than Anniyai Anu Anuvaa Anupavikkiramaathiri Kadhai Onrirunthathu.
Enakku Manathil Orennam, Nam Een Ival Solkiramaathiriyee Seksirkaaka Ivalai Upayokikkakkoodaathu? Avaleethaanee Nammai Kooppiduraal. Ithu En Palli Nanpanin Kaathal Maathiriyalla, Kalloori Nanpanin Kaathalmaathiri! Naamum Avalai Anupavikkalaamena Mudiveduttheen.
anru Muluvathum Avalai Paakka Mudiyavillai. Aduttha Naal Kaalai Kalloori Pokaiyil Pas Sdaappil Avalai Paattheen. Naanga Eppavum Oree Passilthaan Povom. Appoluthu Aval Ennai Kandu Kollaamal Irunthiddaal, Naanum En Kalloori Sella, Avalum Avalin Kalloorikku Senru Vanthaal. Maalaiyum Valakkam Pola Oree Passil Vara, Naan Avalai Paattheen, Aval Avaludaiya Tholikaludan Peesiddirunthaal. Ennai Kandathum Mukatthai Thiruppiddaal. Naanga Pas Sdaappil Erangi, En Veeddirku Seekkiram Vanthiddeen, Aval Veedu Enga Veeddai Thaandithaan Pokanum. Valakkam Pola Enga Veeddil Aalillaathathaal, Naan Kathavukiddeeyee Nirka, Aval Ennai Kadanthu Poka Naan Avalaiyee Sirippudan Paakka, Aval Senriddaal. Pin Naan Veeddirkul Senru Dirash Maatthiddu Veliyee Vara, Avanga Amma Eetho Porulai Enga Veeddil Kodukka Sollum Sattham Keedka, Veliyee Vantha Naan Kathavai Thiranthu Veeddirkul Poyiddeen.
Aval Paavadai, Thaavani Kaddikkondu Vanthaal, Kaiyil Keesari Podda Dappaa Onru Irukka, Aval Athai Engaveeddu TV Kiddee Vaikka, Naan Aval Kiddeeyee Ninreen. Aval Sella Muyanraal, Naan Paaynthu Avalai Kaddiyanaittheen. Aval Thimira, Avalin Kaathil “thivyaa, Mannicheedu, Naanum Yosicheen. Kaathalellaam Veendaam. Enakku Unnai Padukkavechoo Panna Aasaiyaa Irukku. Vaadi Pannalaam” Enru Aval Kaiyai Pidichu, Peendirkul Soruka, Aval Ullangaை En Koddaikalai Varudiyathu. Aval Purinthu Kondaarpola, Ennai Paatthu Sirichaal. Aval Alaku Kannai Parikka, Avalin Thaavanikkul Kaividdeen. Avalin Aappil Mulaikal Jocketdudan Kaiyilpada, Pidichu Kasakkineen. Avalaal En Kaiyinaal Aval Mulaikal Padda Sukatthai Thaangaamal Munaka, Aval Kai En Sunniyai Piditthathu. Appoluthu Aval Amma Kooppidum Sattham Keedka, Aval Ennidam “iru, 5 Nimishatthil Vanthidareen” Ena Solliddu Senraal. Naan Avalai Ethirpaatthirukka, 5 Nimidatthil Kaiyil Putthakangaludan Vanthaal. Mani 4.40 Thaan Aakiyirunthathu. Ammavum, Appavum 6.30 Aaddathaan Varuvaanga. Aval Vanthathum Kathavai Saatthiddu Kaddiyanaitthaal. Naan Appadiyee Kaddiyanaitthu, Avalai Pedroom Thookki Senreen. Appadiyee Peddil Poda, Avalin Pavadai Thookkikka, Avalin Vennirakkaalkal Palapalatthana. Naan Avalin Thaavaniyai Kaladdiyeriya, Aappil Mulaikal Jocketdukkul Aada, Aval Elunthu Ninraal. Naan Appadiyee Nirka, Rendu Peerum Kaddiyanaichikka, Avalin Iduppai Kaiyil Alutthiddu Aval Mukamengum Mutthamalai Polintheen. Avalum Mutthamida, En DiShirtdai Kaladdiyerinthaal. Naan Verum Meeludannirka, Aval Kaddilil Ukkaanthu, En Peend Zippinmeelee Mutthamiddaal. Athilileeyee EnSunni Nimidikka, Peenddinai Kilikka Rediyaayirukka, Avalee En Zippai Kaladdinaal. Jatti Podaathathaal, Sunni Veekamaaka Veliyee Thalaikaadda, Aval Sunniyai Kaiyil Piditthaal.
Antha Alakiyin Kai Paddathum Sunni Meelum, Perukka Naan Aval Thalaiyai Varuda, 100 Vaads Karand Paayntha Maathiri Irunthathu. Naan Appadiyee Nirka, Thivyaa Sunni Muntholai Vilakki, Moddil Mutthamida Aarampitthaal. Naan Sukatthil Munaka, Aval Mella Naakkinaal Sunni Muluvathum Nakkinaal. Aangila Padatthil Varukinra Maathiri Aval Mella Vaaykkul En Sunniyai Sorukinaal. Aval Vaaykkul Sunni Muluthum Senrida, Aval Mella Umpinaal. Enakku Appadiyee Ays Vaaddaril Neenthukinra Maathiri Irukka, Naan Avalin Thalaiyai Pidichikka, Aval En Sunniyai Kuchi Ays Saappidara Maathiri Umpinaal. Aval Vaayil Sunni Thavikka, Avalee Peenddai Kaladdinaal. Naanum Otthulaikka, Aval En Sunniyai Umpiyee Sutthamseythaal. Naan Vilaki, Aval Mun Ammanamaa Nirka Aval En Ammana Kolam Paatthu Rasichaal. Avalai Elunthu Nirka Vechu, Jocketdoodan Aval Chinna Mulaikalai Pisaiya, Avalee Heekkukalai Kaladdinaal. Naan Kaiyedutthathum, Aval Jocket Piriya Aval Braa Aniyaathathaal, Avalin Mulaikal Thalai Kaaddina. Vellai Velee Enriruntha, Antha Aappil Mulaikalai Kaiyaal Pidichu Kasakkineen. Aval Sinunga, Naan Avalin Kaampukalai Thirukiddee, Aval Mulaikalai Kasakkineen. Pin Vaayaal Kaampukalai Sappa, Aval Sukam Thaangaamal Ulara, Naan Aval Mulaikalai Sappineen. En Vaaykkul Aval Mulaikal Muluthumaaka Ullee Sella, Naan Appadiyee Sappineen. Aval Munakal Roomengum Ethaarolikka, Naan Mulaikalai Kasakkiddee Sappineen. Pin Aval Kaaladiyil Mandiyiddu, Avalin Pavadai Naadaavil Vaay Vecheen. Aval En Thalaikalai Varuda, Naan Avalin Naadaavai Avilttheen. Aval Pavadai Vimmik Kondu Kilee Vila, Aval Pundai Kannil Thenpaddathu. Sutthamaa Mudiyee Illaamal, Valuvaluvenrirunthathu. Sikappaa Sirisaa Pilanthiddu, Appadiyee En Kankalukku Virunthu Padaikka, Aval Pundaiyai Nukarntheen. Angee Veesiya Kaama Manam, Manathai Kavara, Naan Aval Pundaiyai Mutthamiddeen. Meelee Aval Sinunga, Naan Aval Pundaiyai Mutthamiddiddee Nakka Aarampikka, Sukam Thaangaamal En Thalaiyai Pidichiddee Sshaaaa Enraal.
aval Pundaiyai Rendu Viralaal Pidichu Pirikka, Avalin Ul Suvarkalellaam Palichena Theriya, Avalin Pundaiyai Nakkineen. Aval Kaama Sukatthaal Eetheetho Moonaka, Naan Kandu Kollaamal Nakkineen. Aval Pundai Udasuvarkalil Avalin Paayaasam Padinthirukka, Naan Mukarntheen.athilirunthuthaan Kaama Manam Aditthirukkira Thenpathai Purinthukondu, Aval Paayaasatthai Suvaittheen. Aahaa! Aval Thantha Keesariyai Vida Inippaaka Irukka, Naan Appadiyee Aval Pundaiyai Nakkineen. Nakka Nakka Inpamaaka Irukka, Naan Aval Pundaiyai Vidaamal Nakkiyee Suttham Seytheen. Avalaal Sukam Thaangaamal, En Thalaiyai Pidichu Ilutthida, Naanga Rendu Peerum Ammanamaa Kaddik Kondom. En Sunni Aval Adivayirril Idikka, Naan Avalai Mutthatthaal Mindum Nanaitthiddu, Avalai Kaddilil Padeekkavaittheen. Aval Kaalkalai Akaddikka Vaitthu Athanul Nulainthu Avalmeel Paravineen. Aval Kannangalil Mutthamidduddee, En Munnaal Kaathali Thivyaavin IlamPundaiyin Meelee Sunniyai Urasineen.
Avalum Kaalkalai Akaddi Kaanpikka, Mella Aval Thuvaaratthukkul Aluttha Aval Sathaikal Rompa Kadinamaaka En Sunniyai Mella Ullee Viddana. Naan Mindum Alutthi Muyarsikka, Avalin IlamPundaikkul En Paathi Sunni Iranga, Naan Appadiyee Sunniyai Urukineen. En Muthal Xsai Anupavikka, Mindum Aval Pundaikkul Kutthineen. Ippothum Atheeyalavu Ulleepoka, Mindum Uruki Uruki Kutthineen. Avalum Sukatthaal Munaka, Enakku Sunnitthol Kilintha Maathiri Irunthathu. Aanaalum En Moddu Avalin Pundai Ul Suvaril Muddumpothu…. Aahaa! Enna Sukam! Enna Sukam!. Naan Atharkaakavee Valiyai Thaangik Kondu, Aval Pundaikkul Kuttha, Oralavu Aval Pundai Ilakiyirukka, Naan Appadiyee Kutthineen. En Mulu Sunniyum Aval Pundaikkul Poka, Naan Konjam Aasaiyil Veekamaaka Aval Pundaikkul Sunniyai Vida, Avalo Sukatthaal Kathara Aarampitthaal. En Sunni Avalin Adi Vayiru Varai Senru Kodi Nadda, Avalo Kathara Aarampitthaal.aval Mukatthai Paatthu Kondee “itharkaakatthaanee Ennai Eemaarrinaay.. Anupavi” Ena Manathukkul Sollik Kondee, Ongi Ongi Kuttha, Aval Sininginaal. Naan En Valiyai Porutthuk Kondu, Aval Kalutthil Mukam Puthaitthu Nakkikkondee Iduppai Thookki Thookki Adikka, En Theevathai Thivyaavin Pundai En Sunni Kutthu Thaangaamal Rappar Maathiri Valainthu Kodutthu Athira, Aval Valiyaal Katharinaal. Naan Avalai Kandu Kollaamal Aval Aappil Mulaikalai Sappik Kondee, Idittheen. Aval Kaampukalai Parkalaal Kadichu Vilaiyaadiddee, Avalai Ottheen. Paavam Sukatthukkaaka Eengiyaval, Athai Anupavippatharkul Setthu Vidukira Maathiri Katharinaal.
Naan Muthal Muthalaaka Kidaittha En Kaama Anupavitthai Muluthaaka Anupavikka, Aval Pundaiyai En Kadappaaraiyaal Ongi Ongi Kuttha Aval Katharal Athikaritthathu. Naanum Vidaamal, Kuttha Thanni Varukinra Maathiri Irukka, Aval Pundaiyilirunthu Iduppai Thookkik Kolla En Sunni Veekamaaka Thanniyai Aval Pundai Meel Koddiyathu. Aval Chitthirap Pundai Meel En Muthal Kaamaneer Paddathaal, Appadiyee Oluka, Aval Paathi Mayakkatthil Padutthirukka, Naan Appadiyee Aval Thaavaniyaal Thudaichi Vida Mani 5.20 Aakiyirunthathu. Aval Kiddeeyee Naanum Padutthukka, Aval Eetho Yosikkira Maathiri Meelee Paatthidirunthaal. Naan Aval Kannatthai Thiruppa Vedkappaddaal.
Naan Avalidam “thivyaa, Rompa Nanridi. Enakku Ithuthaan Muthal Anupavam. Unmaiyileeyee Nee Veliyee Maddumalla Ullayum Alaki Thaandi. Athuvum Un Pundai Summaa Thakkaaliya Veddi Vecha Maathiri Sekkas Seveelnu Kannai Parikkuthudi. Unakku Eppa Ol Veendumaanaalum Ennidam Vaadi” Ena Oree Moochil Solli Mudikka, Aval Sirichaal. Pin Aval Ennidam “thinamum Intha Neeramee Naama Okkalaamdaa” Enraal. Enakkum Sariyaa Pada, Naan Avalai Kaddiyanaichu Mulaikalai Kasakka, En Sunni Niminrathu. Aval Kan Paatthida, En Sunniyai Kaiyaal Pidichu Varudinaal. Aval Varudal En Sunnikku Puthu Sukatthai Thara, Mindum Sunni Perutthathu.
Aval Appadiyee Kaalkiddee Vanthoo Padutthukkondu, Sunniyai Vaaykkil Poddu Umpinaal.
naan Marupadiyum Sorkatthil Mithakka, Aval Thalai Mudiyai Kothividduddee Anupavicheen. Avalukkum Kilarchiyaa Irukka, Naan Aval Umpuvathai Rasicheen. Aval Ennai Nallaa Padutthukka Sonnaal, Naan Eenena Keedka, Aval Solkireenena Ennai Padukka Vaitthaal. En Thalaikku Neeree Thaandu Kaal Podduddu Ninru, Avalee Aval Viralaal Pundaiyai Virichu Kaaddiddee En Vaayirku Neeree Kondu Vanthaal. Naan Purinthu Kondu Naakkai Needdi Nakkineen. Aval Sukatthaal Munakik Kondee, Pundaiyai Virichu Kaanpikka, Naan Aval Viralaiyum Seetthu Nakka Aval Pundaikkul Irunthu Theen Oluka Naan Nakkineen. Suvai Maaraamal Appadiyee Irukka, Naan Muluvathaiyum Nakkiyee Eduttheen. Avalaal Sukam Thaangaamal Vilaki, Appadiyee En Sunnikku Neeree Vanthaal. Aval Mella Pundaiyai Viraachiddee, Sunni Meel Ukkaanthaal. Avalin Thuvaarathukku Neeree Aval Sunni Irukkimaaru Ukkaanthathaal, Aval Pundaikkul Sunni Mella Nulainthathu. Enakkum Puthu Sukamaa Irukka, Aval Mella Ukkaanthaal.
mindum Aval Elunthaal, En Sunni Viriya Appadiyee Sunni Pundaikkul Pokumaaru Ukkaanthu Ukkaanthu Elunthaal. Enakku Sunni Thol Surungi, Surungi Viriya Naan Sukamaa, Valiyaa Ena Theriyaamal Munaka, Aval Sukatthaal Munakikkondee Ennai Padukka Vechu Otthaal. Naan Appadiyee Irukka, Aval Maddum 5 Nimidam Appadiyee Seythaal. Ennaal Aval Mulaikal Aadiya Aaddam Thaangaamal Kai Needdi, Athanai Kasakkineen. Aval Vali Eerpada, Aval Kaiyai Thaddinaal. Naan Vidaamal Aval Thoppulai Paatthiddee, Mulaikalai Alutthi Kasakkineen. Avalukku Sukam Athikamaa Irukka,veekamaaka Katharinaal. Enakku Kanji Varukinra Maathiri Irukka, Avalai Vilakka En Sunniyai Vaaykkul Vechidaal.aval Vaayileeyee Peeychineen.

Kannum Kannum Kollaiyadaithaal (aka) Kannum Kannum Kollaiyadaithal is a Tamil movie with production by FTS Films, direction by Desingh Periyasamy, cinematography by K.M.Bhaskaran. The cast of Kannum Kannum Kollaiyadaithaal (aka) Kannum Kannum Kollaiyadaithal includes Dulquer Salmaan, Ritu Varma.

Thevidiya Kadhai – 1
Tamil Kamakathikal – Thevidiya Kadhai – 1
Tamil Kamakathaikal – Hi, Nan Kavi full name Kavitha. En life la Nan epadi our thevudiyala anandratha pathi dha indha kadhai. Nan Enga oorla govt skl la padichitu irundhan, oralavuku sumara padipan. Enaku apaveaa kaai la konjam perusa irukum skl la toilet pogum bothu en frds la epadi du unaku Mattum perusa irukunu ketu en kaaiya aluthi papanga apavea enaku adila edho panum. En skl la Enga PT sir na elarkum bayam enakum dhan.
Ana Enna matum konjam special ah treat panuvaru.PT sir Ku en Mela Oru kannu ana enaku adhu apa theriyathu. En kita Jolly ah peasuvaru romba pasama iruparu. Ipadiyea konja nal pochu thidirnu Oru nal PT sir ena PT room Ku kooptaru romba dull ah irundharu.
Sir: Ama Kavi Inga va unkita onu solanum, Nan straight ah matterku varan enakunu indha olagathula yarum Ila indha skl la enaku pudicha orea aalu ne dha. I LOVE u Kavi. Nan nalaila irundhu skl Ku varamatan Chennai Ku Poran. Unakum ena pudichi irundha nit kelambi va Nama yarukum theriyama odipoidalam Nan una nalla pathukuran.
Idha ketadhum enaku Oru nimisham ena pandrathunea therila. Andha vayasula onum purila ana avara enaku romba pudikum nit veetla yosichan. Ena pandrathunu theriyama nit 1 maniku kelambi sir veetuku ponan.

064. Thirukkoviloor - Sri Thiruvikrama Perumal Temple
This is one among the "Pancha Krishnaranya Kshetram". Other Ksthremas are Thirukkannankudi, Thirukkannapuram, Thirukkannanmangai and Kabisthalam.
"Oruvar Padukka - Iruvar Irukka - Moovar Nirkalam".
The Thaayar of this sthalam is Poongoval Naachiyar.
Utsavar Thaayar name is Pushpa valli Thaayar.

Kadavul Mangala Vizha
siththaandha selvar, arunootrpulamai aanroar paeraasiriyar daakdar pa. iraaman, avargalin vazihaattudhal peyaril ip paadal yennaip poal yeliyavar padippadhatrku yeatrravaaru piriththu kodukkappattulladhu. ivvaaru piriththu koduppadhu yeliya muraiyil katrruk kolluvadhatrkku mattum thaan payanbaduththappada vaendum. iththudan ippaadalhalin porul kodukkappattulladhu.
aadhiyae amarar koavae. 1
ariya vaedhangal puhazndhu kooruhinra muruhap perumaanae! sivaberumaanae! saravanap poigaiyil thoanriya mudhatrporulae! thaevardham arasae! amudham pera mandhara malaiyai maththaahak kondu paatrkadalaik kadaiyum kaalaththil, tham udambinaal maayangal pala seidha thirumaalin sahoadhariyaana umaiyaalukka uriththaana thamadhu idappaahaththaik koduththuch sivandha sadai asaiyath thiruvarut kooththinaich seiyum netrrik kannanaahiya sivaberumaanukkuk kuzandhaiyae! yen theeya vinaihalaith theerththu arulpurivaai. un sivandha thiruvadihalaiyae nambi vandhaen. yenakku aadharavu oruvarumillai. mayil vaahanaththaich seluththuhinra unnudaiya thiruppeyar mandhiraththai (saravanabava) uraiththa vannam immannulahil oadikkondum aadikkondum thirihinraen. avvaaru thirindhum manaththil kondulla yennaththul oar yellalavu kooda isaindhu varavillai yenru yen ulmanaththil kunamaahaadha kaayam yeatrpattu varundhum yenakku yaar adaikkalam? kooruvaayaaha.
kai kuviththidum yennai un
sanahan, sanandhanan, sanaadhanan, sanathkumaaran aahiya munivargal naalvarukkum melanayoahaththilamarndhu sinmuththirai kaatti nyaanaththai unarththiyaruliya muraippadi, paraasara munivargal pudhalvargalaana thapthar, anandhar, nandhi, sadhurmuhar, parudhi paani, maali aahiya aaru paergalukkum kulirchchi niraindha thirupparangunraththil thanimaiyil (sirandha naanku vaedhangalin andhamaana mudindha porulai vinaihal muzudhum poakki unarththum poruttu), arul vadivaana melanayoahaththil yezundharulich sinmuththirai kaatti nyaanaththai unarththiyarulinaai, meiyarivaalaranri indha unmaiyai ariyavallaar yaar? andha niraivaana kaariyam yenakkum vandhusaera vaendumenru yen kaiyaatr kumbiduhiraen. ahdhu yenru vandhu vaaikkumoa? anbitrku oththa kannaaha ullavanae! maasillaadhu meiyarivaana paerinba maehamae! yennudaiya ullaththullae uvahaiyaai ullavanae! ariya vaedhangal puhazndhu kooruhinra azahiya muruhap perumaanae! sivaberumaanae! saravanap poigaiyil thoanriya mudhatr porulae! thaevardham arasae!
theevira tharap periya karunai seidhu ali ariya
pirammaa, vittunu, uruththiran aahiya mummoorththihalum, irukku, yasur, saamam, adharvanam yenum naanku vaedhangalum, irubaththettu aahamangalum, puraanangalum, idhihaasangalum, thonmaiyaana munivargalum, sivahanath thalaivargalum, muppaththu mukkoadi thaevargalum vananguhinra unnudaiya thiruvadihalin karunaiyaik kondu unnudaiya thiruvadihalaip perudhal yelidhenru unnai nerunginaen. adiyaenmeedhu viruppam kondu, theevira tharappakkuvaththai arulum periya karunaiyaich seidhu kaappaayaaha. arumaiyaana theivaththanmai porundhiya meiyarivaana melanaththil yezundharulum sivaraaja yoahanaai vilangum perumaanae! thavappaerarasanae! uyirgalukkuk kadavulae! arunahiri naadhapperumaanukkuth thiruvarulai aliththaruliya kuruvaai vilangum iraivanae! ariya vaedhangal puhazndhuraikkum azahiya muruhapperumaanae! sivaberumaanae! saravanap poigaiyil thoanriya mudhatrporulae! thaevar tham arasae!

Tamil Kamakathaikal - Saar, Plees Neenga Appadi Solla Koodaathu
Home » Tamil Kamakathaikal » Saar, Plees Neenga Appadi Solla Koodaathu
Saar, Plees Neenga Appadi Solla Koodaathu
enathu Peyar Veenu. Vayathu. 32 Enakku Thirumanam Aakki 5 Varudangal Aakinrathu. Naan Sontha Tholil Seythu Varukinreen. Varukinra Varumanaam Engal Kudumpa Selavukkee Sariyaaka Pokinrathu. Enathu Manaivikku Vayathu 28 . Kaar, Pangalaa Ena Sokusaaka Vaala Veendum Ena Avalukku Payangara Aasai. Aanaal En Tholilil Kadum Poddiyil Iruppathaal Atharkku Thakuntha Varumaanam Kidaikkavillai. Ethaavathu Seythu Perithaaka Sampaariyungal Ena En Manaivi Enna Varpurutthi Kondu Irunthaal. Eppadiyaavathu Panakkaari Aakaveendum Enpathu Avalukku Veriyaaka Irunthathu.
Oru Naal Naan Mathiyam SaapPaddirku Veeddukku Vanthapoluthu En Veeddin Munpu Oru Periya Kaar Ninrukondu Irunthathu. Veeddukkul Senru Paarttha Poluthu Oru Alakiya Penmani Ullee Haalil Udkaarnthu En Manaividam Araddai Aditthukkondu Irunthaal. Enathu Manaiviyin Kalloori Tholi Ramaa Enavum, Oru Thaniyaar Niruvanatthin MLM Maarkedding Seythukondu Irukkinraal Enavum En Manaivi Arimukapadutthi Vaitthaal. Pin Konja Neeram Peesividdu Poyviddaal.
Iravil Naan Padukkaiyil Senru Padutthukkondu Payangara Moodil En Manaiviyai Kaddiyanaitthu Aval Meel Eera Muyanrapoluthu, Aval Ennai Thadutthuviddu, Aval “ennanga, Ivning Vanthaalee, Avangalum Aarampatthil Kaasukku Kashdapaddaanga. Aanaa Ippoluthu MLM Maarkedding Lainil Irangi Niraiya Kaasu Seertthiddaa. Naan Nam Kudumpa Soolnilai Sonnathum , Ramaa Ennai Avanga Kooda MLM Maarkedding Vara Solluraanga. Aval Enakku Ellaa Sapporddum Panraalaam. Niraiya Kaasu Samparikkalaamaam. Naan Aval Kooda Maarkedding Pokaddumaa?’ Ena Keeddaal.
” Maarkedding Lain Ellaam Unakku Puthusu. Rompa Kashdamaana Veelai. Risk Athikam. Veendaam” Ena Naan Kooriyapadi Aval Jaakkaddai Piritthu Aval Mulaiyai Braavil Paartthu Rasittheen. Aval Thiranda Mulaikalin Thiradsi Thaangaamal Braa Thinarikkondu Irunthathu.
“eenga, Muthalil Naan Keeddathukku Sammatham Sollunga, Illainaa Eppoluthum Naan Ungakooda Padukka Maaddeen” Ena Kooriyapadi Aval Plavus Hookkukalai Maaddikondu Kaddilil Kuppira Padutthu Kondaal.
Munpakkam Aalai Kollum Kankalum, En Vaayil Un Thadiyai Vai Ena Alaikkum Kavarchi Uthadukalum, Thiranda Paruttha Mulaikalum, Vimmi Vedittha Pundaiyum Avalukku Munpakka Alaku Enraal, Pinpakkam Paartthaalum Aval Udampu Mika Kavarchiyaakatthaan Irunthathu. Kummenru Siru Malaimukadukalai Ponru Thirandu Iruntha Aval Pinpakka Sathai Kunrukalum, Payangara Nelivukaludan Iruntha Iduppum, Athan Meel Paravalaaka Neendu Kidantha Aval Adarntha Koonthalum, Ennai Veriyeerriyathu. Aval Sonnathai Saathikkum Saathiyai Seernthaval. Aval Viruppatthirku Maruppu Sonnaal, Vaal Muluthum Paddini Kidakkaveendiyathuthaan. Veeru Valiyinri Avalukku Adipanintheen. Udan Aval Mallaakka Padutthu Enakku Kaalai Viritthaal. Anru Iravu Muluthum Sukatthai Enakku Vaari Vaari Valanginaal.
Aduttha Naal Kaalai Ramaa Vanthu En Manaiviyai Kaaril Alaitthu Senraal. Pin Maalaiyil Naan Veedu Thirumpiya Pinthaan, Veedu Thirumpinaal. Piyuddi Paarlar Senru Aval Mukam Marrum Udalai Alakupadutthikkondu Vanthirukkinraal. Pin Thunikkadaikku Senru Oru Dajan Sudithaarkalukku Aardar Thanthu Vanthullaal. Ellaam Raamaavin Selavaam. Maarkedding Sellumpoluthu Smaardaaka Irukka Veendumaam. Ithu Engee Poy Mudiyapokinratho Ena Enakku Kavalai Thonrinaalum En Manaivi Naan Solvathai Kandukollamaaddaal Enpathaal Vaayai Moodikkondeen.
Aval Kooda Antha MLM Pisinas Middingukku Oru Naal Poy Iruntheen. Niraiya Dai Kaddiya Paiyankal Varuvorai Varaveerru Kondu Irunthaarkal. Kaappi, Piskad Ena Payangara Upasarippu. Pin Meedaiyil Silar Thonri Peesa Aarampitthaarkal. Vaalkkaiyil Munneeraveendum Enraal Kashdappaddu Ulaikka Veendum,summaa Irunthaal Kidaikkaathu, Naan Muthalil Kooli Veelaikku Poy Kondu Iruntheen, Intha Pisinas Seyya Aarampitthathil Irunthu, Enakku Pala Lachangal Kidaitthu Varukinrathu Ena Ishdatthukku Kadhai Alanthukondu Irunthaarkal. Ramaavum Angu Kalakala Ena Siritthu Peesikkondu Irunthaal. Raamaavukku Anru Maddum Oru Lachatthukku Meel Sek Kidaitthathu. En Manaivikku Sila Aayirangal Kidaitthathu. Enakku Santhosamaakatthaan Irunthathu.
Aanaalum En Manaiviyin Veekamaana Valarchi Enakku Oru Santheekatthai Eerpadutthiyathu. Oruveelai Kasdamarkalai Pidikka Ethaiyum Seyya Thuninthu Viddaalo Ena Thonriyathu. Nalliravil Aval Veedu Thirumpoluthu, Aval Braa Kalandu, Sudithaarkal Kasangi Iruppathu Theriyum. Vanthavudan Asathiyil Thoongi Viduvaal. Aanaal Aval Ennidam Kaanpikkum Piriyatthil, Padukkai Sukam Tharum Veekatthil Kuraivillaamal Iruppathinaal Ithu Theevaiyarra Karpanai Ena Thonriyathu. Meelum, Tharppoluthulla Sokusu Vaalkkaiyai Ilakka Enakku Manam Illai. Aanaal Naan Ninaitthathu Sari Ena Enakku Oru Naal Thonriyathu.
Oru Naal Enathu Mukkiya Vaadikkaiyaalarudan Oddalil Mathu Virunthil Iruntheen. Avar Niraiya Aardarkal Enakku Tharuvaar. Eekappadda Tholilkal Seythu Mika Vasathiyaaka Iruppavar. Appoluthu Avarukku Oru Pon Vanthathu. Athil Vantha Namparai Paartthathum Ennai Paartthu Kannaditthaar. “paarappaa. Pisinas Maarkadding Pannum Ivaluka Tholla Thaangamudiyalai. Vidaama Ennai Nacharikkiraanga ” Ena Kooriyavaaree, Ponai Lavud Speekkar Poddu Enakkum Keedkumaaru Peesa Aarampitthaar. Ponil Kedda Kural Enathu Manaiviyudaiyathu. “saar, Naan Sinthu Peesareen” “sollummaa ” “saar, Mudivu Panniddeengala… Innaikku Vanthaa Sekku Vaangikkalaamaa? ” “eemmaa, Enakku Ethukkumaa Intha Maathiri Pisinas Veenum? Appuram Ennaal Nee Solrathu Maathiri Ellaam Aal Pidikka Mudiyaathu. Enakku Veendaam Viddudummaa…”
“saar, Plees Neenga Appadi Solla Koodaathu, Aaraayiram Roopaaythaanee Saar, Ungalai Ponra Pisinas Maankalukku Ithellaam Oru Naal Dringa்s Selavukku Kooda Patthaathu ?” “inga Paarummaa, Naan Opanavee Peesareen, Dringa்s Adittha Jaali Kidaikkum Athanaalee, Selavu Panreen, Unakku Selavu Pannunaal Enakku Antha Jaali Kidaikkumaa?” “ennathaan Solreenga?’ “inga Paarumaa, Sutthi Valaichu Peesalai. En Padukkaikku Vaa, Unakku Aaraayiram Enna Athupol Palamadangu Thareen. Vareeyaa ?’ Ena Keedka, Enakku Athai Keedka Avamaanamaaka Irunthathu. En Manaivi Pathilee Peesavillai. “ennammaa Pathilee Illai?” “saar, Naan Neeril Vareen, Angee Peesikkuvom, Naan Engee Vara”
“innaikku Maalai En Pannai Veeddukku Vaa ” Ena Koori Mukavari Koori Ponai Vaitthuviddu Ennai Paartthu Siritthaar. “veenu, Neenga Avalai Vanthu Paarunga, Ennamaa Iruppaa Theriyumaa? Kuspu Thotthu Poyaranum. Appadi Aval Mulaikal Kummunnu Irukkum, Neengalum Vaangaleen, Summaa Avalai Vedikka Paarkathaan.. ” Ena Kooppida, Naan Marutthu Viddu Veedu Thirumpineen.
angu Ithukkaakavee Oru Sokusu Padukkai Arai Ulla Anaitthu Vasathiyulla Veedu Kaddi Vaitthullaar. Maalai Avar Sonna Neeratthukku En Manaivi Skooddiyil Kilampi Viddaal. Pin Iravu Eddu Manikkuthaan Vanthu Seernthaal. Aval Kaddiyiruntha Pudavai Nanku Kasangi Irunthathu. Pilavus Buttonkal Adippakkam Sariyaaka Podapadamaal , Kalandu Aval Vellai Praavai Palichenru Kaaddiyathu. “ennanga, Innaikku Oru Periya Paarathiyai Piditthu Periya Pisinas Seythuviddom. Avar Motthamaaka Patthu Peerukku Undaana Panam Kaddi Viddaar. Meelum Niraiya Peerai Sipaarisu Seyvathaaka Koorinaar ” Ena Kooriyapadi Ullee Padukkaiyarai Senraal. Ullaasamaaka Paadu Paadikkondu Udaikalai Kalainthaal. Nanku Kulitthu Viddu Thoongi Viddaal. Naan Saapideenaa, Illaiyaa Ena Kooda Aval Kavalai Padavillai.
Aduttha Naal Antha Tholil Athiparai Paartthu Naid Enna Nadanthathu Ena Keeddeen, “antha Ponnu Peeru Sinthuppaa, Sooparaa Kampani Kodutthaa. Enakku Vaayil Vaitthu Seyvathuthaan Pidikkum. Aval Vaay Veelaiyil Payangara Keddikaari Pola Irukku.
ennai Urinji Edutthu Viddaal. Enakku Avalai Mikavum Piditthu Poy, Aval Pundaiyai Naan Nanraaka Nakki Eduttheen. Aval Koduttha Sukatthukku Enna Kodutthaalum Idaakaathu. Irunthaalum, Oru Peyya Aardar Kodutthulleen. Innum Koduppeen, Nee Veenumunaa Oru Aaraayiram Roopaay Redi Pannu, Unkooda Padukka Solreen” Ena En Manaiviyai Pukalnthu Thallinaar.
Athan Pin Thinamthorum Kavarchiyaaka Udaiyaninthu Ramaa Kooda Kaaril En Manaivi Veliyil Poyvanthaal. Sila Samayam Neeram Kadanthum Nalliravil Veedu Vanthaal. Maarkadding Veelaiyil Neeram Kaalam Paartthu Veelai Seyyamudiyaathu Enru Ennai Adakkividuvaal. Silamaathangalileeyee Aval Kaiyil Kaasu Purala Aarampitthathai Kaana Mudinthathu. Sonthamaaka Aakdivaa Skooddar, Maaruthi Kaar Ena Vaangikondaal. Ramaa Kudi Iruntha Veeddukku Arukileeyee, Moonru Pedroom Konda Pangalaa Veeddukku Vaadakaikku Kudi Ponom. Theevaiyaana Maadarn Sopaa, Kaddil, Daining Deepil Ena Vaangi Kuvitthaal. Veeddileeyee Oru Thani Araiyai Aapisaaka Maarrikondaal. Veeddu Veelaikku Aadkalai Seertthu Kondu Mulumaiyaaka Pisinas Veelaikalai Maddum Paartthu Vara Aarampitthaal. Vasathikal Perukiyathaal, Naanum En Tholilai Vidduviddu Avalukku Uthaviyaaka Aval Aapis Veelaikalai Kavanitthu Varukireen.
Aval Pundaiyai Kilikka 3

Yaakkai porutha nilam.

Vaazhavarae vaazhathavar.

Marunaal vara nillaa uravugal - Incest/Taboo - Literotica.com
Incest/TabooMarunaal vara nillaa uravugal
Vasanthaavum Gomathium paechchu swaarasyaththil athaik kavanikkavillai. Sameepaththil peytha mazhaikku, neer vazhinthu oaduvatharkaaga, vettappattiruntha oru pallam. Muthalil adi eduththu vaiththaval Vasanthaathaan. Thobukkadeer!
Araikkul utkaarnthu ezhuthik kondiruntha Mahesh, saptham kaettu, vaasalukku oadi vanthaan. Gomathi thigaiththuppoay nintrirunthaal. Mahesh, paaynthoadi vanthu, vizhunthu kidantha Vasanthaavaith thookki vittaan. Avaludaiya udambu nadungkik kondirunthathu. Avalaik kaiththaangkalaaka nadaththi, thaaniruntha araikkul kondu poanaan. Gomathi pinthodarnthaal.
Athu oru factory. Mahesh oru engineer. Avan iruntha office room-ukkum main unit-ukkum nalla idaiveli irunthathu. Idaiveliyil mandik kidantha pullai vetti appurap paduththa vanthavargalthaan anthap penngal.
Vasanthaavin kanngal kalangkivittirunthana. "Adi pattirukkum polirukkae" entraan Mahesh. Aval vaethanaiyaal uthattaik kadiththaal. Avan oru moolaiyil iruntha First Aid box-ai eduththu vanthaan. "Adipatta idaththaik kaattungka, marunthu poadalaam". Anaal avaloa Gomathiyai aerittup paarththaal.
"Adi chee, kaattudee, aapaththukkup paavamillai" entru athattinaal Gomathi. Vayathil periyaval Gomathi. 27 allathu 28 irukkalaam. Vasanthaavukku 22 allathu 23 irukkum. Athanaalum Gomathi athattip paesinaal. Vasanthaa thayangkith thayangkip pudavaiyai uyarththinaal. Adith thodaiyil, innum oru inch uyarththinaal pundai than pokkai vaayaik kaattividum enkira uyaraththil, chiraaippuk kandirunthathu.
Maheshukkum kittaththatta Vasanthaa vayathuthaan. 23 allathu 24. Thuni eariya thodaigalaip paarththu vizhi pithungki vizhiththaan. Aval thodaigal mozhu mozhu entru urundu thirandu irunthana. Echchil vizhungkith thaviththaan. Avan nilaimaiyaip paarhthtu Gomathikku chirippu vanthathu. Aanal chirikkaamal sonnaal, "Payappadaatheengka, sir, thadavungka marunthai".
Avan nadungkum viralgalaal panju eduththu thudaiththu, kalimbu pithukkip poosi vittaan. Appoathu,Gomathi ontru solla, Vasanthaa avalai oangki oru adi vittaal. Gomathi sonnathu ithuthaan: "Ithukkae intha nadukkamnaa, ithukku maela irukkira kaayaththaip paarththeengkanaa..."
Avargal poana piraku athai ninaiththu chiriththuk kondaan Mahesh. Aanal avan pooloa viraiththuk kondu serious-aagi nintrathu.
Maru naal Vasanthaa vaelaikkup poakavillai. Gomathi poayirunthaal. Aanaal avaloadum koodap paesa antru Maheshukku vaayppuk kittavillai. Senior engineer oruvar vanthu utkaarnthu kondu, Maheshaip poala inexperienced engineers kidaikkira vaayppaip payan paduththik kondu experience gain panna vaendum entru upadhesam ceythu kondu irunthaar. Appadi, antru kidaiththa vaayppaiyum payan paduththa vidaamal aruththuk kondu irunthaar.
Atharkku maru naal Vasanthaa poanaal; Gomathi poakavillai. "Kayam aarivittathaa?" entru Mahesh avalaik kaettaan. "Umm" entraal. Atharkkul aval udal ettuk koanalaaga nelinthu valainthathu. Avan thunichchalai varavazhaiththuk kondu, "Paarkkalaamaa?" entru kaettan.
Aval chutrum mutrum noattam vittaal. Piragu, visukkentru room-ukkul nuzhainthuvittaal. Oru moolaiyil poay nintrukondu, than pudavaiyai mulangkaalukku mael uyarththinaal. Avan aval mun mandiyittaan. Irandu paer idhayangalum padapadaththana. Irandu paer udambilum oru nadukkam unndaayitru. Aval maelum thiraiththu, aarik kaaynthupoayvitta than kaayaththaik kaattinaal. Avan nadungkum viralgalaal athai varudinaan. Innum maelae thookik kaanbikka aval kai paraparaththathu. Manam thunichchal atru thayangkiyathu. Aanaal avanukkoa aarvak koalaaru. Kai neenduvittathu. Aan pillai allavaa? Pudavaiyai uyarthaavittaal enna, avan viralugal maeloornthu athai thottuviittana. Uppith thiranda, aavi parakkum, eera uthadugal! Avan viral nunigalaal seendappatta naagap padamaay virinthu, aval pundai, avanaip poadath thudiththathu.

Name : Thiru Neermalai - Sri Neervanna Perumal Temple
In this Sthalam, the Perumal is found is various positions as Nindraan, Irunthaan, Kidanthaan and Nadanthaan Thirukkolam.
* The Perumal shows his 4 sevas in this temple (ie) - Nindra, Iruntha, Kidantha and Nadantha Thirukkolmas.
Moolavar and Thaayar:
* Neervannar - Nindra Thirukkolam.
* Lord Narasimhar - Irundha Thirukkolam.
* Lord Ranganathar - Kidantha Thirukkolam.
* Lord Thiruvikrama - Nadantha Thirukkolam.
Thirunaraiyoor Nindra Thirukkolam
Thiruvaali Narasiman (Irundha Thirukkolam)
Thirukudanthai Aarai Amuthai (Kidantha Thirukkolam)
Thirukoviloor Ulagalanthaan (ThiruVikrama kolam)
* Thirumangai Alwar - 19 Paasurams
* Karunya Pushkarani for Nindra Perumal.
* Sittha Pushkarani for Ulagalantha Perumal.
* Swarna Pushkarani for Veetruntha Paramapatha Emperuman.
* Ranga Vimaanam - Sri Ranganathar.
* Santha Vimaanam - Lord Narasimhar.
* Thoyagiri Vimaanam - Ulagalantha Perumal.

Jap to Sheik: Yendra??? Endra salsa pathi pAeSEpOtta? Naan yAethukuda niruthOnom? "Pune"nu sonna PUna mathiri suthivarum Avaan nirutha solluda Naan nirutharaen. Jap to Sap: Enra PK unra pondatti-kku line kuduppaanda (echos) kudupaanda kudupaanda.
Jap: Enraa sammandhammillaama paesi-pOtta.
Jap to Sheik: Niruthuraaa. Ippadi Sap-kku pvt-a ANUppa vaendiya mail-a group-ukku ANUpradha niruthuraa. Evening light-a tiffin-ra paer-la Hotel Sangeethavaya Oru vaaram close-panradha niruthuraa.

en akka meenaa pundai super story 4 _ Tamil Sex Stories Tamil Sex Story Tamil Kamakathaikal
en akka meenaa pundai super story 4
apdiye akkaa mulaiyila vaai sechchu, kaampai sappa paal kottiyadhu. apdiye urinji kudisittu, akkaavum, naanum divi paakka aarampiththom. akkaavin mulaikal rendum neettidirukka, divi paaththitte mulaiyai thadavinen. akkaavin thaali kazhuththil thonga, naan sirichchen.
“yendaa sirikkire”
“illa thaaliya paaththuthaan”
rendu perum apdiye ukkaandhu divi paaththidirukka, akkaavin kaiyai yeduththu, yen lunkikkul vittitten. aval kai pattathum, yen saamaan nimira, aval mulaiyai kasakkidirunthen. avalum sunniya aatta, okkalaamaa yena kettaal. naan ippa vendaamenrida, aval kaiyeduththittu, diviyai paaththidirundhaal. ippadiye neram kadakka, mani 12 aanathu. yenakku veriyera, lunkiya vilakki, jattiya vilakka, sunni paduththirundhadhu. akkaa yennai paaththaal.
“akkaa kaiyadichchu vidu” yenka, sirichsaal. pin naan marupadiyum solla mella kaiyaala sunniya thottaal. sunni yezhumpida, rendaattu aattinaal.
aval oomba vaai kondu poga, naan maruththitten. avaleem vittuttu sunniya kulukka, yen thanni kottiyadhu. ava kattiyirundha paavaadaiyileye suththama seiya, kuzhanthai azhath thodangiyadhu. akkaa kuzhanthaiyai yeduththu vandhu, apdiye madiyila pottu kuniya, veliye neettiya kalasangal vazhiye, kuzhanthai paal kudichchadhu. appo akkaa “paaruppaa, un maaman nee paal kudikka eesiyaa vazhi panniyirukkaan.” yenka, naane sirichchen. pin kuzhanthai paal kudichchu mudikka, thottilil pottuttu, akkaa samaiyal velaiyai seiya aarampiththaal.
naanum divi paaththidirukka, aduththa arai mani neraththil samaiyal aanathu. akkaa suthanthiramaakave mulaiya kaattittu veettinul ulaava, naanum andha azhakaiye paaththu rasichchen.
rendu perum onnaa ukkaandhe saappittu mudikka, mani 1kku melaakittadhu. aval thoonkalaamenka, naanga rendu perume kattilil paduththu thoonga aarampichsom.
thoonki yenthirikka mani 4 aanathu. rendu perum paatharoom poyi mukam kazhuvittu tee vechchu kudikka, kuzhanthai ala aarampiththaan. udane akkaa paalootta, kuzhanthai kudikka maruththu melum azhuthaan. udane akkaa vilaiyaattaai “intha paaru, intha paaru. maamaa paaru, yaanai maathiri povaaroo paaru” yena, yennai kaiya keezheyoonittu, aval mele ukkaara maathiri ukkaandhaal. naan apdiye nakara, akkaavum nakarndhaal. udane kuzhanthai azhukaiyai niruththittu, sirikka aarampiththathu. udane yenakkoru aidiyaa thoniyadhu.
udane kuzhanthaiyidam “ippo ammaa mela yaanai savaari seiyalaamdaa” yenrittu, naan yezhunthittu, akkaavai kaiya oonittu nirka vaikka, athe maathiraa ninnaal. aval paavaadaiyai mele thookka “dei, yennadaa pannare” yenraal. naan sollarenuttu, avalai kaala virikka solla, avalum seithaal.
pinnaalirundhu aval pundaiya rendu nakku nakkittu, mella lunkiya vilakki, akkaavin pundaiya thadava, aval sukaththila munakinaal. kuzhanthai sirikka, mella akkaa pundaikku pinne mutti pottuttu, akkaa pundaiyai pinnaalirundhu okka, aval munakinaal. naan apdiye yezhundhu kuninjittu, ava pundaikkul kuththa, apdiye nakarndhaal.
kuzhanthai yaanai savaariyena sirikka, naan yen vilaiyaattai vilaiyaada, saamaan thanniyai seekkiram kakkittaan. naanum thanniya akkaavin paavaadaiyileye thodachchi vittittu yezhoondhu poga, akkaa kuzhanthaikku vilaiyaattu porul koduththittu vanthida, rendu perum kitte kitte ukkaaththu divi paaththom. pin akkaa yenthirichchu samaiyalaraikku poyida, naan mattum divi paaththidirunthen. akkaa adikkadi veliye varum pothum vilaiyaattookku avalai kooppittu paavaadaiya thookki kaatta solli, pundaiyila muththamiduven. pin akkaavin sooththai kaatta solli, killi vaippen, ippadiye vilaiyaada daim 7 aanathu.
akkaa samaikkap poyida, naan akkaavidam senren. yennataanu akkaa ketka, naan paattukku kunindhu paavaadaiya thookki pundaiya nakkinen. akkaavum ஸ்ஸ்ஆஆ yena munakitte, samaiyal velaikalai seithaal. akkaavin pundaiyila thannivanthathoom nakki kudisittu yezhundhu poyiduven. akkaavum kamminu vittuduvaal.
ippadiye iravu saappaadu rediyaayida, rendoo perum saappittu mudichsom. aval petroom pokalaamenka, naan paathroom poyi kakkoos ukkaanthittu vanthen. varum podhu aval naittikku maariyirukka, naan kaththiyeduththu avalin mulaikalitaththilum, pundaiyitaththilum vetti vida siriththaal. yeppavum naan paakkanum yenka, aval purinthavalaai sirisitte sariyenraal. thinamum kattilleye paduththu poradikka, anru kattil kadiyila paai virichchu paduththom. yen ippadinu ketka, naan ithu sinna idam, inka oththaa soopparaayirukkumnu ankeye paduththu avalin dirasai kazhattaamaleye oththen. apdiye oththittu thoonkitten.
aduththa naal aval velaikku kilamba, naan leevu poda vechchen. aval anrirunthoo naan solvathaik ketka aarampiththaal. yen michcha leevu naatkalai yenkakkaa meenaa pundaiya oththe kazhikka, kaalej naatkal thodangina.
appaavidam kettu akkaa veettilirundhe kaalej poi vara aarampiththen. thinamum ozh poduvathaal yen vaazhkkai santhoshamaak kazhiya, yen meenaa akkaavum, naanum kanavan, manaivi maathiri vaala aarampiththom. naan sonnaal nadu rottilayum pudavaiya thookki kaatta, akkaa rediyaayirukka, yen machsaan paavam jeyilila vaazhkkaiya kazhichsittirundhaan.
naan akkaavidam saththiyame vaankitten. aval purushan vanthaalum, avanukku theriyaamal nichsayam yennai okka vendumena, avalum yen sunni kuththukalukku aasaippattu, saththiyam seidhu thanthida, thinamum yen meenaakkaavin pundaiyil yen iravukal sukamaakak kazhikindrana. yen meenaakkaathaan yen ulakam.
karuththukal varaverkappadukindrana.

idhu kANmin annaimIr! ikkattuvichchi sol koNdu nIr
ik kattuvichchi – thiruchchandha viruththam 64 “kANilum uruppolAr” (not even qualified to be seen).
sol koNdu – thiruchchandha viruththam 64 “sevikkinAdha kIrththiyAr” (unpleasant to hear about).

Tamil Kamakathaikal - Ava Purusan Nallaa Ongi Ongi Kuttha, Saavitri Ennaiyee Paatthaal
Home » Tamil Kamakathaikal » Ava Purusan Nallaa Ongi Ongi Kuttha, Saavitri Ennaiyee Paatthaal
Ava Purusan Nallaa Ongi Ongi Kuttha, Saavitri Ennaiyee Paatthaal
kiraamam Enpathaala Anneeramee Aal Nadamaaddamillaama Irukka, Mella Saavitriyakkaavin Veeddu Kathavai Thalla, Thiranthiddathu. Naan Poonai Maathiri Aval Veeddirkul Nulainthu, Avanga Pedroom Kathavai Mella Thalla, Konjam Kashdamaa Irunthathu. “kir” Enra Melliya Satthatthudan, Kathavu Thiranthukka, Naan Poonai Maathiriyee Kiliruntheen. Mella Thalai Thookki Paakka, Saavitriyakkaavin Meelee Raviyannan Purandiddirunthaar. Saavitriyakkaa Arai Thookkatthilirukka, Avanga Pudavai Vayirrikku Meeleeriyirunthathu. Raviyannan Saamaan Aval Thuvaaratthirku Kilee Muddiddirukka, Naan Elunthuninreen. Saavitriyakkaa Ennai Paatthiddaal. Aval Kankal Viriya, Satthamidaveendaamena Saikai Kaaddineen. Raviyannan Apdiyee Muddidirukka, Avar Sunniyai Naanee Edutthu Thuvaaratthin Meelee Vecheen. Avar Apdiyee Ekki Ekki Idikka, Akka En Mukatthai Paatthiddee Munakinaal. Ava Purusan Nallaa Ongi Ongi Kuttha, Saavitri Ennaiyee Paatthaal. Aval Mukam Sukatthaal Viriya, En Saamaan Nadduddathu. Raviyannan Sarru Neeratthil Thanniyai Aval Pundai Meelee Thelisiddu, Apdiyee Uranginaar. Saavitriyakkaa Avarai Thalli Padukka Vaikka, Avar Nanraaka Thoonginaar.
Naan Mella Kathavai Thaaliddiddu, Saavitriyakkaa Kiddee Nadanthuvara Avanga Than Purusan Paayaasatthai Thodachidirunthaanga. Thudaikka Veendaamena Kaiyai Thadutthuddu, Veekamaa Jattiya Muddi Varaikkum Kaladdi Viddidaddu Veekamaa Aval Meelee Padarntheen. Paduttha Veekatthula Ava Saamaanla Sorukiddu, Iyanga Aarampittheen.
saavitri “s.vaaaa..aa…” Ena Munaka, Aval Mukatthil Veritthanamaa Mutthamiddeen. Aval Sirisiddee Munakaludan Paduthirukka, Naan Veekamaa Idikka Aarampittheen. Sirichidiruntha Aval Mukam Maara, Apdiyee Aaddiyaaddi Adicheen. En Koddaikal Aval Kundi Oddai Meel Paddu Therikka, Naan Enakkeerpadda Ellaa Valiyaiyum Porutthiddu, Idicheen. Aahaa..! Rompa Naal Kalichu, Ottha Sukatthila Rompavum Aaveesamaa Okka, Aval Kanavan Ethuvumee Theriyaama Kudipothaiyil Thoongidirunthaan. Naan Ava Purusan Mukatthai Paatthiddee, Saavitriyakkaa Pundaiyila Okka Rompavum Inpamaaka Irunthathu. Pin Avalai Elunthu, Kaddilil Naay Maathiri Irukka Vaikka, Aval Kanavan Kan Mun Aval Kundi Needdeeddu Irunthathu.
athan Mun Mandiyida, En Saamaan Kundiyai Thadaviyathu. En Thadiyai Kaiyila Pidichu, Ava Pundaikkul Soruki, Mella Muthukai Munnum Pinnum Thalli Iyanga, Aval Marupadiyum Theevadiyaa Maathiri Munaka Thuvanginaal. Eppadiyaavathu Aval Kanavanukku Theriyaama Marupadiyum Saavitriyakkaavai Anupavitthira Maaddomaa Ena Eengiya Enakku, Aval Kanavan Munneeyee Aval Pundaiyai En Saamaan Vilungiddirunthathu.
Aahaa! Enna Sukam. Enna Sukam. Intha Maathiri Soolnilaiyila Okkirathenpathu, Sorkkatthula Ukkaanthiddu Sooppu Saappidara Maathiri Thitthippaa Irunthathu. En Saamaan Avalin Adi Vayitthula Kutthi, Thaitthiddu Vara Saavitriyakkaa Uyiree Pona Maathiri Aadinaal. Pin Eetho Ninaitthaval Avalin Mukamarukee Iruntha Ava Purusan Lungiyai Vilakkinaal. Ava Purusan Saamaan Surungi Kidakka, Athaiyedutthu Viralaala Uruddinaal. Pin Veri Pidicha Maathiri Antha Sunniyai Kasakka, Ava Purusan Dappena Thirumpi Padutthaan. Naan Unmaiyileeyee Payanthee Poneen. Aanaalum Oppathai Nirutthavillai. Inpam Panmadangaaka Irukka, Appadiyee Idichiddee Iruntheen.
atharku Meelee Thaanga Mudiyaama, Saamaanai Veliyedukka Ava Pundai Meeleeyee Thanniya Koddineen. Pin 5 Nimidam Rendedutthiddu, Mindum Avalai Okka Thuvangi, Pundaikkul Saamaanai Sorukineen. Appadiyee Meelum 2thadavai Thanniya Koddiddu, Diras Edutthu Maaddineen. Aval Mukam Santhosatthila Malara, Ennai Ammanamaaka Valiyanuppi Vaitthaal.
Naan Mella Kathavai Thirakka, Aal Nadamaaddamillaiyena Uruthipadutthiddu En Veeddai Vanthadaintheen. Vanthathum Aval Pundai Niyaapakatthileeyee Thoongiyum Poneen.
Aduttha Naal Valakkam Pola Veelaikku Poneen. Kaalaiyee Saavitriyakkaavai Paakka, Mukam Malarnthirunthathu. Anru Veelaiyum Nalla Vithamaaka Odiyathu. Anru Maalai Eppavum Pola, Veelai Mudinthu Veeddirku Vantheen. Vanthathilirunthu Aduttheppadi Avalai Okkalaamena Manathinul Thiddam Poda, Iravu Aakiddathu. Iravu Saappaadum Thayaaraakida, Appadiyee Saappiddu Mudicheen. Aanaa, Konjam Saappaadu Athikamaa Saappiddiddathaala Thookkam Varalai. Athanaala Apdiyee Summaa Padutthukidantheen. Sari Kadaikkaavathu Poyiddu Varalaamena Kilampi Poneen.
Kadaiyila Oru Palam Vaangi Saappiddiddu, Veeddirku Vara Raviyannan Kadaiyila Ninrirunthaar. Ennai Paatthathum Ennudaneeyee Vanthaar.
Avar Ennidam “mutthu… En..na… Mannichirudaa.”
“illadaa Unnai Patthi Theriyaama, Naan Unnai Thappaa Ninaichiddeendaa.”
Naan Eethum Theriyaatha Maathiri “ennayaa, Enna Ninaicheenga”
“athu Veendaam, Vidu. Aanaa Neetthaikku Neethaan Ennai Kadaittheruvilirunthu Veeddila Viddeyena Kadaikkaarar Sonnaar. _thinanthorum Tamil Derddi Stories Padiyungal_avar Kidda Keedkum Pothu Mothallayee Pala Tharam Neethaan Ennai Veeddila Viddeenaar. Athaan… Ini Adikkadi Veeddirku Vaadaa.”
Naan Eethum Theriyaathamaathiri “enakku Onnum Puriyalanee” Enka, En Veedu Vanthiddathu. Avar Avar Veeddukku Poyida, En Veeddirkul Vanthideen. Enakku Ellaam Puriya, Avaree Saavitriyakkaavai Inimee Okka Sammatham Koduttha Maathiri Irunthathu.
Athanaala Thinamum Veelai Mudinthu Vantha Piraku, En Ishdappadi Saavitriyai Avanga Veedleeyee Otthukkareen. Avalidam Keedka, AvaPurusan “ini Kudikkamaadeen, Avalai Santheekapadamaadeen” Ena Sonnathaaka Sonnaal. Naanum Santhosamaa Avalai Okkireen. Ennaalthaan Intha Maarramena Avalum Inpamaa Virichu Kaadduraal.
Ennathaan Naanga Veeddinul Pannaalum, Vaaramorumuraiyaavathu En Thoddathula Avalai Okkareen. Intha Mutthuvin Kutthu Epdiyena,en Thodda Sedikalukku Theriyum.
Neenga Keeddu Paakkareengalaa!

health tips, Udal nalam kappom, Udal nalam kurippugal
Kalleeral pirachanai arikurigal - Symptoms of Liver Disease, Udal nalam kurippugal, Udal nalam kappom, health tips in tamil, liver damage symptoms in tamil
Kalleeral pirachanai arikurigal - Liver damage symptoms in tamil
Manidha udalileye kalleeral than mikapperiya uruppu.
Enave kalleeralil siru pirachanai enraalum, athanaal udalin palveru seyalpaadugal paadhikkappadum.
Athilum kalleeralil ulla pirachanai mutrinaal, uyiraik kooda ilakka neridum.
Enave kalleeralil pirachanai irunthal thenpadum arikurigalai ovvoruvarum therintu kolla vendiyatu avasiyam.
oruvarukku kalleeral sariyaaga seyalpadaamal irunthal, kaalkalil lesaaga veekkam avvappotu erppadum. Enave thideerenru kaalgal veengiyirunthal, udane marutthuvarai santhikkavum.
eppotu oruvarin sarumam matrum kangal manjal niratthil irukkiratho, atthagaiyavarukku manjal kaamaalai kaaranamaaga pitthaneer thenkiyullathu enru arttham.
kalleeralil kattigalaanathu avvalavu seekkiram varaathu. aanaal kalleeralaanathu theeviramaaga paatikkappattirunthal than, kalleeralil kattikal uruvaagum. Ungal kalleeralil kattikal irunthal, valathu pakkatthil adivayitrirku satru mele vali eduppathodu, vayiru uppusatthudanum irukkum.
Vaanti, sorvu, kaaichal
kalleeralai virus thakkinaal uruvaavathu than hepatitis ennum kalleeral alarchi. Ungalukku kalleeral alarchi irunthal, vaanthi, sorvu, kaaichal, mayakkam, kulir ponravatrai santhikkakkoodum.
Alcohol kudippavaraaga irunthal, viraivil kalleeral paathikkappadum. Alcohol athigam paruki kalleeral paathikkappattirunthal, thalaichutral matrum kulappam adikkadi erpadum.
kalleeral sariyaaka iyangaamal iruppin, kumattalai santhikkakkudum. Enave unkalukku avvappotu kumattal erpatthal, udane marutthuvarai santiyunkal.
kalleeralil pirachanaigal irunthal, ungal siruneer adar manjal niratthil velivarum. Enave intha nilaiyai neengal sandhitthaal, thavaraamal marutthuvarai santhiyungal.
naalpatta sorvu kooda kalleeral pirachanaikkaana arikuriye. aagave ungalukku adikkadi sorvu erpattal, marutthuvarai santhitthu muraiyaana parisothanaiyai merkondu, sariyaana kaaranatthaik kandariyunkal.

Paadal Petra sthalangal, Divya Desangalum Thiruthala Yathiraiyum, Abhimana Talangalin Vazhikatti, Arumuganin Thiruppugazh Thalangal, Sakthi Thalangalin Vazhikatti,

A small booklet on Pancha Brahma Thalangal is also published. On 1.1.2014 Vetri Tharum Velvan Thalangal and book of historic murugan temples but not listed in Tiruppugazh was also published. On 9.2.2014 a book titled Sugamalikkum Suriya Vazhipadu which is an encyclopedia of Sun and 90 temples connected with Sun are listed.

Konjamaaka Mayir Vari Theriya Uppalaaka Iruntha Mathanameedukal Naan Thinikkum Pothu Innum Uppiyathu. Ippoluthu Avalin Pothai Kurainthirukka Veendum Allathu Kaamam Athikamaayirukka Veendum Avalaakavee Iru Thodaikalaiyum Akaddi Vaitthuk Kondu Iduppai Uyartthik Kaadda En Irumput Thadi Ponru Viraitthu Ninra Sunniyai Aval Pundaikkul Aalamaaka Nulaittheen. Unmaiyil Asvini Pundaiyai Vida Daiddaaka Irunthathu. Aval Moochiraitthapadi “deey Pangi Ennadaa Panree. Unnuthu Rompa Daiddaa Irukkudaa” Enraal. Naan “ethukkaa Daiddaa Irukku-” Enrathukku Piravinaa “ayyo Pangi Un Sunni Rompap Perusudaa En Pundaikkullee Daiddaak Kutthuthudaa” Enrathum Naan Veriyudan Veekam Veekamaaka Okka Aval “aang 8230 aang 8230 nallaak Kutthudaa Pangi.. Nallaa Eerudaa” Enru Anattha Palanimidangal Avalai Eeri Itthanai Naal Theekki Vaitthiruntha En Semanai Aval Koothi Valiya Valiya Ootthividdu Uruva Michamiruntha Seman Aval Mulai Varai Iramaakkiyathu. Ippoluthu Avalukku Pothai Murrilumaaka Akanru Viddathu Enru Ninaittheen. Ennai Vedkatthudan Kaddip Piditthu Anaitthu En Vaayil Mutthamiddu ”deey Pangi Innikkutthaan Naan Muthanmuthalaa Otthathu Maathiri Irunthuchudaa” Enraal. Konja Neeratthil Naanum Avalum Irandaavathu Aaddatthai Aarampitthom. Piravinaa En Kaathai Nakkiyapadi “pangi Itthanai Naal Illaama Eppadidaa Innikku Thunichaloda Ennaip Poddee” Enrathum Naan Antha Maatthiraiyaip Parris Sonneen. Appuram Anriravu Muluvathum Naanum Piraveenaavum Oruvarukkoruvar Pinnip Pinainthu Kidanthu Otthom. Ithu Sila Naadkal Thodara Aduttha Maatham Avalukku Thooram Ninru Viddathu. Avalai Vida Mamavukkutthaan Makilchi Athikam. Athan Pin Piravinaa Sani Naayiru Naadkalil Ennai Varavalaitthu Ennudan Inpamaaka Oltthu Varukiraal. Appothu Mama Ooril Illaathapadi Eppadiyaavathu Areenja் Seythu Vidukiraal. Senra Sanikkilamai Iravu Naanum Avalum Otthuk Kondirukkum Pothu Piraveenaa Ennidam ”pangi Annikku Kodutthiyee Antha Maatthirai Irunthaa Ippa Kodeen. Athu Poddukkiddu Otthaa Kikkee Thanippaa” Enraal. Anraikkup Paartthu Antha Maatthirai Ennidam Illai. Aduttha Vaaram Varum Pothu Eppadiyum Maatthirai Kondu Vanthu Irandu Peerum Podduddu Okkalaam Enru Solliyiruntheen. Aanaal Mallikaa En ஃprandidam Maatthirai Keeddatharku Ippothu Kedupidi Athikam Enpathaal Kidaikka Villai Enkiraan. Thayavu Seythu Antha Maatthirai Naakarkovil Kanniyaakumari Pakkatthil Engu Kidaikkum Allathu Entha Daakdar Antha Maatthiraikku Piraskiripshan Seeddu Maruppinrit Tharuvaar Enra Thakaval Enakkut Therivikkavum. Enakkaakavum En Anpu Akkavirkaakavum Intha Uthaviyai Seyyummaa Enru Manraadik Keedduk Kolkireen Mallikaa. ___________pangajkumaar. Pangajkumaar Nee Neeril Irunthirunthaal Ongik Kannatthil Arainthiruppeen. Avvalavu Aatthiram Vanthathu. Pothai Maatthiraikalukku Naan Eppoluthumee Ethiri. Ithee Pakuthiyil Pothai Maatthiraikku Adimaiyaana Oru Ilampen Vipasaariyaaka Maara Neeridda Avalatthinai Eluthiyirukkireen. Nee Anru Un Akka Piravinaa Mithu Aasaippaddu Avalai Otthathaik Kooda Naan Eerruk Kolveen. Aanaal Thodarnthu Avalukku Antha Maatthiraiyinaip Palakkappadutthividaathee Unnai Manraadik Keedduk Kolkireen. Avalin Veriyinai Athikarikka Un Poolai Maddumee Payanpadutthu. Un Mama Avalai Unnalavirku Thirupthiyaaka Okkaathathaal Thaan Unakku Thodarnthu Pundaiyaik Kaaddi Okka Vidukiraal. Marroru Mukkiyamaana Vishayam. Sariyo Thavaro Itthanai Naal Kulanthai Illaamaliruntha Piravinaa Nee Otthathaal Karuvurrirukkiraal. Nichayamaaka Antha Maatthirai Itthanai Naal Kalitthu Karuvurrirukkum Piraveenaavin Udalnilaiyaiyum Mukkiyamaaka Anthak Karuvinaiyum Mikavum Paathikkum. Oonamurra Kulanthaiyaakap Pirakkum Vaayppukal Mika Athikam. Enavee Intha Ennatthai Adiyodu Kaividdu Vidappaa. Unnaik Kenjik Keedduk Kolkireen. Piravinaa Antha Maatthiraiyinai Virumpinaal Kooda Athu Karuvinaip Paathikkum Enru Edutthus Solli Avalai Olppathil Manasai Maarri Thodarnthu Inpam Kodutthu Vaa Pangi. Piravinaa Unnudan Okkum Pothu Sarru Maarupadda Pothaiyum Theevai Athu Irunthaal Innum Veriyaaka Okkalaam Enru Viruppap Paddaal Alavodu Iruvarum Oyin Maddum Kudikkalaam Thappillai Pangi. aarampatthil Kannatthil Araiveen Enratharku Oru 26 2011 1 11 Majaa Mallikaavidam Keelungal. 2.0 . . .

Tamil Kamakathaikal - Majaa Mallika Kathaigal 349
Home » Tamil Kamakathaikal » Majaa Mallika Kathaigal 349
— Engalin Kaathal Theyvam Kaamtthin Valikaaddi Mallikaa Naan Kanavilum Ninaitthiraatha Oru Peeralakiyai Okkum Vaayppu Kidaittthu. Appoluthuthaan Aankalai Vida Penkal Ninaitthaal Than Aasaikku Ukanthavanai Eppadiyaavathu Valaitthup Poddu Otthu Viduvaarkal Enpathaip Purinthu Kondeen. En Nerungiya Nanpanin Manaivi Amirthavarshini. Adikkadi Avan Veeddukku Selveen. Kaapi Kondu Vanthu Koduppaal. Oru Punnakaiyodu Sari. Naanum Avalaipparri Entha Oru Thappaana Ennamum Kondirukkavillai. Naan Avan Veeddirku Sellum Pothu Ennai Anna Murai Vaitthut Thaan Alaippaal. En Veeddirkum Avarkal Vanthirukkiraarkal. Athuvarai Entha Oru Salanamum Inritthaan Naan Iruntheen. Anru Oru Naayirrukkilamai Avan Veeddirku Senriruntheen. Avan Veeddil Illai. Amirthaa Maddum Thaan Irunthaal. Avan Engee Enru Keeddtharku Thideerena Avan Thangaiyidamirunthu Pon Vantthaakavum Athanaal Pengaloor Senriruppathaakavum Sonnaal. Naan Senriruntha Pothu Amirthaa Nakaikal Eethuminri Palaiya Selaiyaikkaddi Thalaimudiyai Vaarichuruddi Kondaiyaakap Poddirunthaal. Athu Oru Maathiri Kavarchiyaaka Irunthathu. Naan Aval Kondaiyai Verippathaip Paarttha Amirthaa “ennai Theechu Kulikkalaamnu Iruntheen. Antha Neeram Paatthu Neenga Vanthuddeengannaa” Enraval Thodarnthu “eennaa Ennaip Paakka Asingamaa Irukkaa-” Enraal. Naan “see See.. Unmaiyila Ippa Rompa Alakaat Theriyaree” Enreen. Aval Meelaakku Sariya Jocketdil Muddum Mulaikalaik Kaaddiyapadi “appadinnaa Een Summaa Irukkinga 8230 Vaanga” Enru Ennai Nokki Kaiyai Needda Naan Avalaik Kaddip Piditthu Anaitthu Vaayil Mutthamiddeen. Naan Veriyudan Avalaik Kaddi Anaikka Aval En Kundiyaip Piditthu Ilukka En Sunni Peendil Muddikkondu Aval Thodaiyidukkil Idittthu. Amirthaa Mokanamaaka Siritthapadi “ppaa.. Ippavee Ippadi Mudduthee Unga Raadu.. Kaaminga” Enrapadi Viru Viruvena Thanathu Aadaikalaik Kalaintheriya Naanum Aviltthu Vida Enathu Neenda Sunniyaip Paartthapadi Aval Ammanamaaka En Mun Amarnthaal. Antha Alakai Ennavenru Solvathu Vaarichuruddiya Kondaiyudan Alavaana Mulaikal Ponga Alakaaka Ennaip Paartthu Siritthaal. En Viraittha Poolaik Kaiyaal Pidittha Amirthaa “etthanai Naal Aasai Theriyumaa-” Enravalai Saritthu Aval Pundaikkul Naakkai Viddu Nakkineen. Aval Pundaiyil Amutham Surakka Nakki Eduttheen. Aval “Anna Thaangalai Vaanga Ennais Seyyunga” Enrapadi Kuninthu Thavalnthu Nirka Naan Kaalaimaadu Eeruvathu Pola AvalKoothiyil Eeri Ottheen. Aval Iduppai Asaitthu Asaitthu Idikka Naan Veriyudan Otthu Aval Pundai Valiya Valiya En Semanai Ootthineen. Avalaikkaddiyanaitthu “amirthaa Ennaala Nampavee Mudiyalai. Eppadi En Kooda Okka Aasai Vanthuchu-” Enreen. Aval Vedkatthudan En Kalutthil Mukam Pathitthapadi “cheey Eppadi Pachaiyaap Peesareenga..” Enratharku “pachaiyaap Peesarathum Oru Verithaan Amirthaa Eppadi Engooda Nee Okka Vantheennu Enakkee Aachariyamaa Irukkummaa. Inthap Penkaloda Mana Aalatthaip Purinjukkidavee Mudiyalai” Enreen. Aval “ippa Ennoda Aalatthaip Paatthuddeengalla” Enrathum Naan Vidaamal “entha Aalam Amirthaa-” Enrathukku Aval Vedkatthudan “en Pundai Aalatthai Paatthuddeengalla” Enraval Elunthu En Sunniyai Appdiyee Iratthodu Umpinaal. Aval Vaayil En Sunni Iruppathu Aval Mukatthai Innum Alakaakak Kaaddiyathu. Naan Veriyudan Aval Vaayilvida Aval Alutthamaaka Sappi Umpinaal. Enakku Thannimuddik Kondu Vanthathu. Veekam Veekamaaka Asaitthu Ullee Vida Sila Nimidangalil En Poolilirunthu Seman Peeriddu Adikka Aval Vaay Nerri Ingellaam En Venney Paalaaka Valiya Siritthaal. Ennaikkaddip Pidittha Amirthaa “ennannee Anni Manjulaavai Okkirathai Vida Ennai Otthathu Nallaayirunthuchaa-” Enraal. Naan “mm 8230 Athusari Naan Otthathu Sureesh Okkirathai Vida Nallaayirunthuchaa-” Enratharku Aval “m 8230 Avarum Nallaa Veriyodu Oppaaru” Enraal. Piraku Enakku Saamaan Demparaakivida Thirumpavum Amirthaavin Pundaiyil Ottheen. Pin Drassai Aninthu Kondu Purappadum Poluthu Amirthaa Vaayil Mutthamiddu “amirthaa Naama Thodarnthu Okkanum Amirthaa Athukku Enna Panrathu-” Enreen. Aval Mokanamaaka Siritthapadi “neenga Manasu Vachaa Naam Thodarnthu Viruppam Pola Okkalaam Anna” Enru Solli Ennai Anuppi Vaitthaal. En Pendaaddi Manjulaavum En Verikkeerra Ol Alakithaan. Irunthaalum Amirthaavai Otthathum Aval Itthanai Naalil Anru Avalaakavee Valiya Ennidam Vanthu Ennai Okkaviddathum Enakku Athisayamaaka Irukkirathu. Amirthaavin Seyalukku Enakku Sariyaana Vilakkam Kidaikkavillai. Avalee Than Purusan Sureesh Nanraaka Veriyodu Olppaan Enru Sonnaal. Appadi Than Purushanudan Pothumaana Olsukam Kidaitthum Ennudan Een Amirthaa Okka Vanthaal Ena Viyappadaikireen. Penkalin Mananilaiyinai Sariyaakap Purinthirukkum Kaamaraani Mallikaa Unnaal Thaan Itharku Thakuntha Vidai Tharamudiyum. ________rattheeshkumaar Rattheesh Itthanai Naal Palakiyum Entha Salanatthaiyum Eerpadutthaatha Amirthaa Thideerena Unnai Mayakki Okka Viddirukkiraal Enpathu Unakku Viyappaaka Irukkirathu. Atthodu Amirthaavin Purusan Avalukku Pothumaana Sukam Alitthum Unnidam Aval Okka Vanthathu Unakku Aachariyamaaka Irukkirathu. Enavee Thaan Inthap Penkalin Mana Aalatthaip Purinthu Kolla Mudiyavillai Enru Solkiraay. Oruveelai Anru Nee Un Nanpanai Santhikkas Sellum Poluthu Amirthaa Seksuval Moodil Irunthirukkalaam. Perumpaalum Penkal Kulikka Rediyaaki Thalaimudiyaik Kondaiyaakas Soruki Oru Alangolamaana Udaiyil Irukkum Poluthu Therintha Aankal Vanthuviddaal Oru Seksi Mood Uruvaaki Avanudan Okka Veendum Enra Aasai Vanthuvidum. Antha Vakaiyil Anru Amirthaa Nee Vantha Poluthu Unnaip Paarttha Antha Neera Aasaiyil Unnudan Okka Vanthirukkalaam. Aanaal Ithai Vida Veeru Oru Kaaranam Enakkut Thonrukirathu. Unmaiyileeyee Amirthaa Thiddamiddut Thaan Unnudan Otthirukkiraal. Amirthaavum Aval Kanavanum Un Veeddirku Vanthirukkum Pothu Un Alaku Manaivi Manjulaavaiyum Santhitthirukkiraarkal. Appothu Un Olraani Manjulaavaip Paartthu Avalai Okka Aasaippadda Un Nanpan Sureesh Ithanai Amirthaavidam Solla Athanpin Amirthaavum Manjulaavum Thiddamiddu Purusankalai Maarrik Kondu Okka Mudivu Seythirukkiraarkal. Athanpadi Anru Amirthaa Nee Vantha Poluthu Unakku Than Pundaiyai Okkk Kodutthirukkiraal. En Ninaippu Ennavenraal Nee Amirthaavai Otthuk Kondiruntha Athee Neeratthil Sureesh Un Manaivi Manjulaavai Otthuk Kondirunthiruppaan. Ippaditthaan Nadanthirukkum Enpathu En Mudivu. Meelum Nee Purappadum Poluthu Thodarnthu Amirthaavai Okka Veendum Enru Sonna Pothu Aval “neenga Manasu Vachaa Naam Thodarnthu Viruppam Pola Okkalaam Anna” Enru Sonnathan Sariyaana Arttham Ennavenraal “neenga Manasu Vachu Manjulaavai En Purusan Okka Anumathitthaal Neengal Ennait Thodarnthu Okkalaam” Enpathu Thaan. Manasu Vaitthaal Enru Solvathan Sariyaana Arttham Ithuthaan. Nee Ithanai Jaadai Maadaiyaaka Sureeshidam Sollippaar. Avan Nichayam Ivarkal Podduk Konda Thiddappadi Nadanthullathu Enpathanai Eerruk Kolvaan. Appuram Enna Irandu Olmannarkalum Manaivikalai Oree Peddil Poddu Maarri Maarri Okka Veendiyathu Thaanee. Atthai Pundai Thakaatha Uravu Tamil KaamakKadhaikal Mamiyaar Mamiyaar Pundai 17 2011 8 00 Majaa Mallikaavidam Keelungal. 2.0 . . .

Nagaichuvai nadigar nagesh avargalin thannambikkai varthigal _ Good thoughts of Comedy actor Nagesh, Actor Nagesh avargalin thannambikkai , Tamil thoughts, arignar karutthukkal, Tamil comedy actor interview in FM radio station,
Nagaichuvai nadigar nagesh avargalin thannambikkai varthigal _ Good thoughts of Comedy actor Nagesh
Vaanoli pettiyondril nagesh: niyayamaaga ungalukku varavendiya nalla peyar mattravargalukku sellum podhu ungalukku eppadi irukkum?
Nagesh: Naan kavalai padamatten sir. oru kattadam kattum podhu, savukku maratthai mukkiyamaa vachu saaram katti, kurukku palagaigal pottu adhan mela pala sitthai ninni kaikku kai kaal maari kattadam uyarndhu konde poi pala aandugalukkup piragu adhu midindha piragu, andha kattidatthirkku varna jaala vitthaigal ellaam adicchu keela irangum podhu kattadam kattuvadharkku mukkiya kaaranamaa irundha savukku maratthai avizhtthu irakki vittu, kiraga piravesatthandru savukkai udharithalli vittu vaazhai maratthai vaitthu thaoranai seivaargal, athanai perumaiyum vaazhai maratthirkku poividum.
idhil ulla unmai enna theriyuma? andha vaazhai maram moondru naal vaalkkai thaan vaazhum. aadu maadugal meyum. kuzhandhaigal pittheduppaargal. piragu kuppai vandiyile poi serum.

Direcor Suseendhiran who has given hits like Vennila Kappadi Kuzhu, Naan Maahan Ella and this time with Rajapattai avar romba sodhapitanga. Onnumai padathula seri illai screenplay, story, direction ellam romba sodhapitaru. I am still in a confusion how come a good director like Suseendhiran could come up with a mokkai padam like Rajapattai. Songs paruvayillai rendu song nalla irunthathu micha song lam okay. But song lam padathoda sync ai agala. Padathula song vantha epo thaan mudiyum nu irunthathu. Action lam comedy ah irunthathu Vikram romba effort pottaru for action but they have make the action into comedy. Example Superman mathri paranthu paranthuopening la lam adiparu namma Vikram athu comedy ah irunthathu but climax kitta action lam okay ya irunthathu. Cinematography was neat.
Overall Rajapattai is a Worst film of director Susennthiran and Vikram. Rajapattai romba mokkai padam padam start to ending namma mind la odura oru thougt epo thaan padam mudiyum. Rajapattai padatha romba mokkai ya irunthathu.
Verdict : Rajapattai entha pettai layum nikkathu

Angee Oru Pallikkooda Vaatthiyaar Kudiyirunthaar. Naan Ponapothu Avar Ooril Illai. Marunaal Kaalaiyil Thaan Varuvaar Enrum Irunthu Kaalaiyil Vaadakaiyinai Vaangis Sellumaaru Avar Manaivi Koorinaal. Avalukku Vayathu 45 Irukkum. Aal Kummenru Irunthaar. Iduppil Irandu Madippukalum Periya Theengaay Size Mulaikalum Poosanikkaay Kundikalaiyum Paarttha En Kaama Manasil Oru Veelai Anriravu Avalaip Poda Vaayppu Kidaikkumo Enru Nappaasai Thonriyathu. Anru Iravu Enakku Dipan Kodukkum Pothu Aval Aduppadiyil Thosai Suda Oru Veelaikkaarakkuddi Athaik Kondu Vanthu Enakkup Parimaarinaal. Avalukku Vayathu 18 Irukkum. Maaniram Maampalam Ponra Kaaykal Kavarchiyaana Utdukal Sirikkum Kankal Ena Alakaaka Irunthaal. Naan Avalai Jollu Viduvathaip Paartthu Aval Kurumpudan “ennanga Neenga Ithuvarai Ponnungalaiyee Paatthathillaiyaa- Ippadi Mulungiraappula Paakkareengalee” Enru Keeli Seythaal. Oru Murai Enakku Thosai Vaitthuviddut Thirumpum Pothu Pad Ena Aval Kundiyil Oru Thaddut Thaddineen. Aval Siritthapadi Ullee Odi Viddaal. Ellaa Veelaiyum Mudinthu Padukkap Ponom. Ennai Avarkalathu Kaddilil Padukkas Sonnaal. Appoluthu Pangajam Ennidam “enna Thampi Anthak Kuddi Sornaavai Rompa Said Adicheengalaamee ava Sonnaa. Enna Thampi Aasaiyaayirukkaa-” Enraal. Naan Ippdi Opanaakak Keeddthum Enakku Enna Seyvathu Enree Theriyavillai. Mavunamaaka Iruntheen. Sornaavum Ullee Vanthu Siritthapadi Ninraal. Aval Thodarnthu “ithula Enna Vanthuchu Thampi Ithellaam Aampalaip Pillaikku Iyarkai Thaanee M.. Avalukkum Aasaithaan.. Sari Neenga Avalaip Podanumnaa Naan Keekkara Keelvikku Sariyaa Pathil Sollanum” Enraal. Naan “m..” Enrathum Aval “sornaa Saamaanla Mayiru Irukkaa Illiyaannu Sollunga” Enraal. Enakku Thookki Vaarip Poddthu. Aval En Thayakkatthaip Pokkumaaru Varpuruttha Naan “m.. Ava Saamaanla Mayiru Konjamaa Irukkum” Enreen. Udanee Pangajam “m.. Paappamaa- Dee Sornaa Un Saamaanaik Kaaddudi” Enraal. Sornaa Entt Thayakkamum Illaamal Paavadaiyait Thookkip Piditthapadi Avalathu Pundaiyaik Kaaddinaal. Avalathu Pundaiyil Naan Sonnathu Polavee Alavaaka Konjamaaka Karu Mayir Irunthathu. Pangajam Avalidam “eey Sornaa Thampi Aasaippaduthu Paaru Ellaatthiyum Avutthudduk Kaamidi” Enrathum Sornaa Ellaat Thuniyaiyum Avutthuddu En Mithu Vilunthu Anaitthaal. Pangajam “Thampi Neenga Avurunga” Enrathum Naan Poddiruntha Kailiyai Avutthu Vida Viraippaaka Ninru Kondiruntha En Sunniyai Sornaa Uruva Pangajam Avalidam “eey.. Evvalavu Alakaa Irukku. Athai Umpudi “ Enrathum Sornaa Avalathu Chinna Vaayil Enperiya Sunniyait Thinitthuk Kondu Umpinaal. Naangal Iruvarum AmmanakKundiyaaka Irunthaalum Pangajam Ethaiyum Avukkavillai. Pin Sornaavai Padukka Vaitthu Aval Pundaiyai Nakkas Sonnaal. Naan Paditthathu Paartthathu Ivarrai Ninaivil Vaitthuk Kondu Sornavin Koothiyai Nakkineen. Aval Pundaiyil Thaamaraippoo Vaasatthudan Kasinthu Kondirunthathu. Pin Aval Mallaanthu Padutthuk Kolla En Viraittha Poolai Aval Sithiyil Nulaitthu Okka Aarampittheen. Kaddilin Thalai Maaddil Amarnthu Konda Pangajam Naan Avalai Eerum Pothu “m.. Appaditthaan Thampi Nallaa Avalai Olunga.. Kutthunga.. Neenga Kutthura Kutthula Ava Pundai Kiliyanum.. M.. Adinga..” Enru Solla Naan Veekam Veekamaaka Otthu En Thanniyai Viddeen. Sari Aduttha Ravundu Pangajatthai Okka Saansu Kidaikkum Ena Ninaittheen. Konja Neeratthil Enakku Sunni Vidaitthuk Kolla Naan Methuvaaka Pangajatthin Kaiyait Thoddeen. Aval Padakkena Ilutthuk Kondu “m.. Athu Veenaam.. Sornaa Pundaithaan Rediyaaka Irukkee. Athulayee Olunga.. Namakku Ithellaam Pidikkaathu” Enru Solli Viddaal. Anru Iravu Naan Naanku Murai Sornaavai Olppathaip Pakkatthil Irunthu Paartthu Rasitthaal. Avalai Eppadi Ellaam Okkanum Enpathai Pachaiyaakas Solli Ennai Veriyeetthinaal. Aanaal Avalai Okka Ennai Anumathikkavillai. Ithu Enakkup Puriyavillai. Innorutthiyai Okka Viddu Athaip Paartthu Rasikkum Aval Een Thannai Maddum Okka Anumathikkavillai. Eppadi Athaip Paartthu Viddu Okkum Aasai Varavillai. Pangajam Aadaikalaiyum Avilkkavee Illai. Naangal Iruvarum Olppathai Veedikkai Paarttthodu Sari. Ithu Enna Vakaik Kaamm- Neethaan Thelivu Paduttha Veendum Mallikaa. ________suntharavathanan Ayyo Anput Thampi Suntharavathananukku KuddipPundai Sornaavai Okka Kidaittha Saansai Vida Pangajatthin MurapPundaiyil Okka Mudiyavillaiyee Enra Kavalai Thaan Athikam Irukkirathu. Pangajam Evvalavu Veriyudan Unnai Sornaa Pundaiyil Okka Viddu RaChitthirukkiraal. Ithu Oru Vakai Vaayurism Enraalum Aval Than Aadaikalaik Kooda Avilkkaamal Pakkatthil Irunthaal Enpathu Konjam Idikkirathu. Oruveelai Aval Irukkum Pothee Sornaavaitthaan Nee Said Aditthathaalum Aval Kundiyil Thaddiyathaalum Veendumenree Unnai Alaikkalitthirukkalaam. Olppathai Rasitthaalum Thaan Pirarudan Okkaatha Patthini Enru Kaaddik Kolvatharkaaka Irukkalaam. Allathu Anru Aval Udalnilai Olkka Eerrathaaka Illaamal thooram Aakiyirukkalaam Irunthirukkalaam. Aval Unnai Okka Vidavillai Enraalum Nanraaka Sunni Pundai Enru Pachaiyaakap Peesiyirukkiraal. Enavee Oru Veelai Naan Solkirapadi Nadanthaal Pangajatthin UppiyaPundaiyil Unakku Okka Vaayppu Kidaikkalaam.adutthamurai Nee Aval Veeddirku Sellum Pothu Sornaavai Eeredutthum Paarkkaathee. Pangajam Unnidam “ennappaa Sornaavai Innikkum Okkariyaa-” Enru Keeddaal ”naan Atharkaaka Onrum Varavillai Unmaiyil Aunty Enakku Ungalai Okkanumnu Thaan Aasai. Annikku Naan Vanthuddup Ponathilirunthu Enakku Unga Ninaipput Thaan. En Aasaiyappurinjukiddu Neenga Vantha Naan Ungalai Okkareen. Illinnaa Naan Poreen. Sornaavai Okka Naan Varalai” Enru Sol. Aval Unnai Sothippatharkaaka Sornavai Ammanamaakki Pundaiyaik Kaaddiyapadi Nirka Vaitthaalum Nee Sornaavait Thodaamal Iru. Aval Unmaiyil Un Aasaiyaip Purinthu Kondu Unnai Okka Viduvaal. Appuram Enna Avalathu Theengaay Mulaiyaiyum Poori Pola Uppiyirukkum Pundaiyaiyum Nanraaka Anupavi. Ithu Nadanthu Viddaal Atharkappuram Chinnakkuddi Sornaavaiyum Kaamaraani Pangajatthaiyum Pakkatthil Pakkatthil Padukkavaitthu Irandu Pundaikalaiyum Eeka Kaalatthil Anupavikkalaam. Pesd Aaஃp Lak Sunni Vathanan . 4 2010 12 30 Majaa Mallikaavidam Keelungal. 2.0 . .

Guyyeeppe, aylletettay yaa iitiis. Afirkkaappe Amarkkaa efiidi aylliyaa bayzziyoogee 16tta xeetu layttappe 19tta xeetu laytta gakkanaassi aybippenne aaruwan wodhiya zalˈˈiyaappe issuwaa. Issi dirijjitee qonccissidoogaadan, ‘25 miilooneppe 30 miiloone gidiya attuma asaa, macca asaanne naata asay gubaayidi bayzziis.’ Issi issi asay yootiyoogaadan, Atlanttike Abbaa pinttiyo wode xeetu shaˈan qoodettiyaageeti hayqqiis. Olaˈuda Ekiweˈana giyo etappe attida ayllee, “Maccaasaa yeehoynne hayqqana haniyaageetu oolee keehi yashsheesinne yootanawukka keehi metees” yaagiis.
Geeshsha Maxaafay “Godaa nu Xoossaa maatan naaqoi” baynnaagaanne i laamettennaagaa gidiyoogaakka yootees. (2 Hanidabaa Odiya 19:7; Milkkiyaasa 3:6) Xoossay Yesuusa kiittidoy, ‘qashettidaageeti birshshettanaagaa, qassi qohettidaageeti qohuwaappe kiyanaagaa yootanaadaana.’ (Luqaasa 4:18) Hegee aylle gidida ubbay laˈa kiyees giyoogee? CHii gidana. Yesuusi kiitettidoy nagaraanne hayquwaa aylletettaappe asaa laˈa kessanaassa. I guyyeppe, “Tumatettai inttena ailletettaappe kessana” yaagiis. (Yohaannisa 8:32) Ha wodiyankka, Yesuusi tamaarissido tumay daro ogiyan asaa laˈa kessees.—“ Dumma Aylletettaappe Laˈa Kiyiyoogaa” giya saaxiniyaa xeella.

Sari Vidunga, Naanee Ellaatthukkum Pothuvaa Sollareen.
Intha Nakaratthula En Muthalaali Peerai Sonnaa, Theriyaathavan Yaarumirukka Maaddaanga. Appeerppadda Ravudithaan En Muthalaali. Ravudiyusam Maddumilleenga, Kadda Panjaayatthu Inna Pira Tholilkal Senju Polaikkira Kandaaroli Pasangalla En Muthalaaliyum Oruvan. Ennadaa Appeerppaddavarnu Solliddu, Ippadi Kedda Vaartthaiyaala Thiddareenuthaanee Paakkareenga. Ada, Muthalaaliyunaa Avanukku Valathu Kaiyo, Idathu Kaiyo Maathiriyilleenga Naan. Avan Kesd Haavusla Irukkira Chinna Chinna Veelaikalai Paakkura Veelaikkaaranga Naan.
En Peeru Saranraaj. Enakku Ippo Vayasu 24 Aakuthunga. Intha Vayasilee Padikkiratha Vidduddu, Kashdappaddidirukkum Aalillaatha Anaathaithaan Naan.
Aam. Ellaa Pasangalai Polavee Naanum Chinna Vayasula Thuruthuruvena Pallik Koodam Poyiddu, Rompavum Jaaliyaathaanga Iruntheen. Engammaavukkum, Engappaavukkum En Meelee Paasam Athikam. Naanthaan Avangaloda Oree Paiyan Enkirathaala Ennai Rompavum Sellam Kodutthu Valatthaanga. Engappaa Ippa En Muthalaaliya Irukkiravan Kiddee Adiyaala Veelaikku Irunthaar. Ennathaan Veliyee Sollikka Mudiyaatha Veelai Thaan Ennappaavukku Enraalum, Pothiyalavu Panam Kidaichathaala Engappaavukku Appothaikku Athuthaan Perithaakap Paddathu. Athanaal Naangalum Entha Vithamaana Siramamum Illaama Irunthom. Enakku En Palli Nanparkaludan Jaaliyaaka Oor Sutthiddum, Eppavum Santhosamaa Vilaiyaadiddumthaan Irukka Pudikkum.
Aanaa, En Santhosam Unmaiyileeyee Antha Kadavulukku Pudikkavillai Enruthaan Solla Veendum. Aamaam, Kadavul Ennudan Vilaiyaada Aarampitthaar.
Naan 7vathu Padichiddirukkaiyila, Vakuppil Paadam Nadanthidirukkum Samayam. Deechar Paadam Nadatthidirukka, Aluvalaka Veelaiyaal Orutthar En Deecharidam Vanthu Kaathil Eetho Otha, Deechar Kannil Kannirudan En Kiddee Vanthaar. Naan Ennavena Avangamukattha Paakka, Avanga Ennai Paiyedutthuddu Veeddirku Poka Sonnaanga. Naanum Ennavena Theriyaama Kilampi Poka, En Veeddil Niraiya Kooddam Ninrirukka, En Perror Oru Kaar Vipatthula Iranthiddathaaka Sonnaanga. Enakku Enna? Eethu? Ena Yosichu Paakkarathukkul En Perror Udal Savakkidangu Poy Seernthiddathu. En Paddi Ennai Valarkkum Poruppai Eetthukka, Enga Veeddai Vitthiddu Avanga Veeddil Valarntheen. Ellaam Kannimaikkum Neeratthula Nadanthumudiya, Enakku Ellaam Kanavu Maathiriyirunthathu. En Appavin Irappu En Muthalaalikku Therinthida, Avar Oru Naal Enga Paddi Veeddirku Vanthirunthaar. Ennai Maathiri Enga Paddikkum Yaarumillai, Engathaatthan Muthalileeyee Iranthiddaar. Athu Maddumillaama Enga Paddiyum Antha Muthalaaliyin Veeddila Veelai Seypavalthaan Enpathaala, Akkaraiyaa Visaarikka Avan Vanthirunthaan. Enga Veeddai Paatthavan, Enga Paddiyidam “inimee Neenga Veeddiveelaikku Veendaam, Enakku Kesd Haavus Onniruku. Anga Veelaikku Yaarumillai, Vaadsmeen Maddum Thaan. Anga Neenga Thangi, Veeddu Veelaiya Kavanichukkunga. Adikkadi Yaaraavathu Vanthaa, Avangalukku Upasaranai Pannanum. Athu Poka Sampalam Athikamaa Thaareen” Ena Solla, En Paddiyum Enna Seyvathena Theriyaama Sammathichiddaal. Naanga Anrilirunthu En Muthalaaliyin Kesd Havusil Veelaikku Ponom. Aanaalum Athu Periya Pangalaa Maathiri. En Padippum Keddu Poyida, Naanum Veeddu Veelaikal Seyya Aarampittheen.
Angee Eppaavathu Sila Penkal Varuvaanga. Pin En Muthalaali Varuvaar, Matthapadiyelaam Sollikkira Maathiri Aadkal Vara Maaddaanga. Athanaala Enakku Avvidam Sorkkam Maathiri Irunthathu. Yaarumillaa Pala Neerangalil Athu En Sorkkapuri.
Varudangal Oda, Pinputhaan Angee Enna Nadakkirathena Therinjikka Aarampittheen. Angee Varum Penkal, Vilaiyathikamaana Vipachaarikal.
en Muthalaali Eppaavathu Vipachaara Viduthikku Pokaiyila, Alakaa Evalaavathu Irunthaa Kaasu Kodutthu Ingee Vaangi Vanthiruvaanaam. Aanaa, Avaluka Vanthathum Oroo Roomil Viddu, Antha Roomai Muthalaali Pooddiruvaan. Engeeyum Veliyee Vidaama, Antha Saaviyai En Paddiyidam Kodutthiddu Poyiduvaan. Pin Eppa Veendumo Vanthu Panniddu, Avalukalai Anuppichiruvaan. Een Avalukalai Pooddurathunaa, Avan Pannarathukkul Avaluka Veerevanukkaavathu Kaalai Virisiddaa, Athaan.
Ithu Theriya, Naan Ivveelaiya Verukka Aarampicheen Enraalum Sotthukku Veeru Valiyillai. Ippadiyee Naadkal Kadakka, Enakku Vayasu Aaka X Areemukamaanathu. Kaiyadippathum, Piddu Padam Paappathum Palakkamaaka En X Unarvai Eppadiyaavathu Theetthukka Aal Kidaikka Maaddaangalaa Ena Eengi Thirintheen. Veliyee Theevadiyaalkal Kidaippaalkal Enraalum,enakku Payam Athikam. En Veeddirkee Theevadiyaalkal Varukiraalkal, Pirakenna Ena Manasu Oru Aydiyaa Kodutthaalum, Angee Varupavalkal En Muthalaaliyin Theevadiyaalkal. Avanukku Maddum Therinjuthu, En Sunniyai Veddi Naduvooddula Alakup Porul Maathiri Thonga Viddiruvaan.
Sari, Atha Maddumaa Pirachinai. Koodavee Paddi Veeru Irukkiraal, Avangalukku Therinjathenraal Ennai Angee Irukkavee Vida Maaddaal. Udanee Angirunthu Anuppi, Veerengaavathu Thangikka Solliduvaal. Athanaal Konjam Adakkiyee Vaasikka Veendiya Nilaimai Eerpaddathu. Aanaalum Vayasu Aakaaaka, En Sunniyin Aripput Thanmai Athikamaakik Kondee Ponathoo. Eppadiyaavathu Oru X Kidaichidaathaavena, Naan Eengit Thavikka Aarampikka, Kadavul Ithaiyee Saakkaaka Vechu Ennudan Vilaiyaada, Rediyaanaar. Appothaan Enakku Athisayamonru Nikalnthathu.
paarpvarkal Anaivarukkumee Sunni Thookkiddaadum Alavukku, Alakiya Ponnorutthiyai En Muthalaali Kooddeedduvanthaan. Aval Mumpaik Kaari Enpathu Maddum Thelivaa Therinthathu. Vellai Kalaril Veedee Vellaiyura Vanthavalai, En Muthalaali Roomirku Kooddeeddu Ponaan. Maalai Neeram Enpathaala Paddi Konjam Pangalaa Munnirukka, Naan Samaiyalaraikkul Oleenthirunthu Avalai Paakka, Avanga Maadi Roomirkul Ponaanga. Enakku Sunniyila Maniyadikka, Vakkira Putthi Vanthathu. Avanga Poyi 5 Nimidam Kalichu, Poonai Maathiri Maadip Padiyeeri Angee Poneen. Kathavu Saatthiyirukka, Appadiyee Ninreen. Konja Neeratthil “aa..aa..sulo…” Ena Munakal Sattham Maddum Vara, Enakku Aananthamaayirunthathu. Ol Podum Satthatthai Keedkavee Avvalavu Sukamirukka, Athaip Paatthaa Eppadiyirukkum, Ada Paakkaratha Vidunga Namma Otthaa Eppadiyirukkumnu Rasichu, Antha Ol Satthatthai Keeddiddirukka Paddi Varukira Maathiri Sattham Keeddathu. Naan Payanthadichu Maadippadiyeeri, Daappookku Poyiddeen. Angirunthu Eddi Paakka Paddi Varuvathai Paattheen. Avanga Vanthathum Veliyee Kilampa, Naan Kilee Vanthideen. Aasai Munakalkal Vanthiruddirunthaalu, Payam Vanthudichu. Athanaala Kilirangida Arai Mani Neeram Kalichu Muthalaali, Antha Roomai Pooddeeddu Kilee Vanthaan. Vanthavan Paddiyidam Saaviya Kodutthiddu “kadaiyilirunthu Naiddu Saappaadu Vaangeekkinga. Avalukku Kodutthirunga, Neengalu Eethaaveenumnaa Vaangi Saappidukunga” Enriddu Kilampiddaan.
Appidiyee Neeram Poyida, Mani 7aaka, Paddi Kiddiruntha Oru Kadaiyila Antha Pennukku Saappaadu Vaanga Poneen. Valakkam Pola Antha Kadaikkaarar Naan Vanthathum Paarsaledutthu Kodukka, Vaangiddu Engalukkum Saappaadu Vaangeeddu Veeddirku Vara, Paddi Enga Paarsalai Samaiyalaraiyila Vaikka Solliddu, Antha Paarsalai Vaangeeddu Thanniyudan Ava Roomukkul Poyiddaal. Naan En Saappaaddai Saappiddu Mudikka, Paddi Vanthaal. Aval Saappiddathu Poka Micha Sikkan Pees Edutthu Vanthu Enakku Saappida Kodukka, Naan Saappiddeen. Paddiyum Avanga Saappaaddai Saappiddu Mudikka Neeram Kadanthathu.
9 Manikkaadda Paddi Thoongida Poka, Enakku Sunniyila Maniyadikka Aarampichathu. Avvalavu Alakaana Pennai Kandathum, Aval Kadal Naduvil Irunthaalum Evanukkum Okkat Thaan Manam Varum. Naanum Appaditthaan. Paddi Thoongi Viddathai, Urithi Seythiddu Mella Elunthu Maadikku Poneen. Angee Antha Penniruntha Kathavai Thoda, Mella Thiranthu Kondathu. Paddi Eetho Niyaapakatthula, Kathavai Poodda Maranthida Naan Mella Ullee Vantheen. Antha Alaki Porvaiya Ilutthu Pottheeddu Thoongeedirukka, Udal Nadukkamaa Irunthathu. Aanaalum Manasu “payappadaathadaa, Payappadaathee” Ena Vadiveelu Dailaakkai Solliddeerunthathu. Athanaala Ava Kidda Mella Poyi, Ava Mukatthai Paakka Kulanthai Maathiri Thoongeedirunthaal. Mella Ava Porvaiya Pidichilukka…..aahaa..!
Chinna Paniyan Poddiddu Paduthirunthaal. Innukonjam Porvaiya Kilirakka… Adadaa Jattithaan Poddirunthaal. Aval Kaalkal Kokku Kaal Maathiri Venmaiyaayirukka, Thodai Maddum Palapalannu Minnuchu. Mella Ava Thoppulai Varudineen. Entha Asaivumillaama Ava Paduthirukka, Enakku Sunni Neeree Thookkiyathu. Kankal Kilee Poka, Ava Jattiyai Noddamiddeen. Thodaiyidukkin Oramellaam Theriya, Pundaip Pilavu Maddum Maraichiddirunthathu. Kan Mun Entha Pundaiyum Paakkaatha Enakku, Athai Paakka Aasaiyaayirunthathu. En Kaiyaal Aval Jattiya Pidichu Oramaa Othukka, Antha 0 Vaads Pavar Velichatthula Naan Paakkum Muthal Pundai.
aahaa! Alakaa Uthaddai Pilanthiddu Ninnidirukka, En Kannil Paal Vadinthuchu. Ennavoru Sikappaana AlakupPundai Avalukku!
Ava Pundaiya Paattha Santhosatthula, Manasu Santhosam Thaangaama Mukattha Maddum Mun Needdi Ava Pundaimeel “is”nu Oru Muttham Koduttheen. Avvalavuthaan… Dappena Enthirichaval, Ennai Kandathum Thidukkiddu Paatthaal. Aval Elunthathum Enakku Payamaayirunthuchu. Naanum Kaddilai Viddu Vilaki Payatthudan Aval Mukatthaiyee Paatthidirukka, Avamukam Saanthamaanathu. Enakku Payam Innum Pokalai. Avathan Udampa Moodiruntha Porvaiya Vilakki, Avalee Jattiyoda Saida Vilakki Pundaiya Kaaddinaal. Aval Ennai Okka Kooppiduraanu Enakku Purinjuthu. Payattha Thookkiyerinjiddu Ava Munnaal Mandiyida, Ava Jattiya Appidiyee Pidisirunthaa. Enakku Ava Pundaiya Nakkanumnu Aasaiyaarunthuchu. Ava Pundaimeela Mukattha Vechu Nakkineen. Muthalla Entha Unarvum Enakku Theriyala. Ava Maddum “ssaaaa”nu Munakunaa. Konja Neeratthula Ava Pundailirunthu Paayaasam Olukuchu. Atha Nakkinathumee… Aahaa…oho… Enna Suvaidaa Ithu. Amirthamee Naakkila Padda Maathiri Irunthuchu.
Thideerena “deey Naayee”nu Oru Kural. Ava Mukattha Nimirtthu Paattheen. Ava En Muthuku Pinnaadi Paakka, En Paddi En Sard Kaalara Pidichu Thookkinaanga. Naan Payatthula Avanga Mukattha Paakka, Ongi Oru Arai Viddaanga. En Paddikidda Naan Vaangiya Muthaladi. Naan Apdiyee Nirka Ennai Pidichu Veliyila Thalla, Ava Jattiya Moodikkiddaa. Paddi Avakidda Mannippu Keeddiddu, Veliyeevanthu Marupadiyum Rendarai Viddaanga. Meelum “muthalaalikku Therinjaa Konniduvaandaa” Ena, Ennai Maadipadiyirakki Avakidda Marupadiyum Mannippu Keeddiddu, Roomai Pooddeeddu Vanthaanga. Vanthaval En Kidda Niraiya Arivurai Solliddu, Thungena Pakkatthula Padutthaal. Naanum “kudutthu Vachathu Avvalavuthaanu” Paduthirukka, Thookkamee Varalai. Paatroom Poyi Ava Pundaiya Ninaichu Sunniya Veliyedukka, Thanni Athuvee Olukiddathu. Pin Roomukkuvanthu Thoongiddeen.
Aduttha Naal Kaalai Elunthu Valakkamaa Veeddu Veelaiya Paatthidirukka, Muthalaali Vanthaan. Vanthavan Neeree Anthapennoda Roomukku Poka, Konja Neeram Kalichu Maadip Padiyirangi Vanthaan. En Kiddee Vanthu Ninnu En Mukatthai Veri Pidicha Maathiri Muraichaan. Naan Eethum Peesamaa Payathudan Tharaiya Paatthu Ninneen.

machaa, yaaminiya oththaa yeppadiyirukkum 3
Mikap Periya Theeviravaathi Yaar Tamil A Jokes 294

Inthirani Arul, Author at Inthirani

magow (cf. gaey) {gaey} v.i. Yaen ni yi bea saap naag ban'ean ni kea yaen nga ba yaang, fa daan naang ko quw ea baay riy. To look for, search, seek.
maqathuk (cf. qathuk-) a. Wagaagëy ngea yaen boech nga fadik' boech ni daab ku ni naang faan. Fa ngoongoliy ea kaet ngea thilthiil ea gi ni qimmoey ba yaang ngea ba yaang riy. Mixed, confused, shuffled (of cards).
Fa rea baarkoow ea kea kireeb ea masiin riy bea yaen u laan ea mathaaw i yaen ni daariy beaq ni ma naang ea gi ni baay riy.
Mu maen mu maaraay naag ea yaer ko chaaq neam, nga ni yaen ni bayuul naag fa rea tiir ngaay.
Faqän raa qey mea yaen ea bitiir ko maeluuk nga laan ea maath'.
Kea yaen ea maen' ko fa rea meeloer nga ba yaang.
Mu pagpaag ea meel ko laay roodow yaa bea yib ea thaam nga laang.
Gabuul ea gu raa yaen gu toey ea paan u baang i muqut roog.
m'aar a. Yaen ea ngunnguun nga fadik' i doewngiy ngea kireeb naag rogon ea paer yaa bea qamiith baang u fadik' i doewngiy fa bea magaaf. Sick, ill.
m'oor ea magael (cf. magael (m'oor + magael)) n. Ba m'uw ni yi maa yaen riy ko magael goeg u reegur. Torch fishing canoe. m'oor + magael
